20Congressional%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20California%20Secretary%20of%20State's%20office%20on%20Friday%20said%20Fong%2C%20who%20had%20previously%20filed%20to%20run%20for%20reelection%20in%20the%20Bakersfield-based%2032nd%20state%20Assembly%20district%2C%20could%20not%20run%20for%20the%20soon-to-be-open%20congressional%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFong%20had%20initially%20declined%20to%20enter%20the%20congressional%20race%2C%20as%20many%20observers%20expected%20state%20Senator%20Shannon%20Grove%20to%20jump%20into%20the%20contest.%20But%20after%20Grove%20passed%20on%20a%20run%2C%20Fong%20changed%20his%20mind%20and%20filed%20to%20succeed%20McCarthy%2C%20for%20whom%20he%20previously%20served%20as%20a%20district%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcCarthy%2C%20who%20was%20ousted%20as%20speaker%20in%20October%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-mccarthy-lost-speakership-cbs-interview-angered-democrats-votes-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eafter%20a%20tumultuous%20nine-month%20stint%3C%2Fa%3E%20leading%20the%20chamber%2C%20endorsed%20Fong%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20last%20day%20for%20candidates%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20race%20was%20December%208%2C%20which%20was%20also%20the%20candidate%20filing%20deadline%2C%20so%20Fong%20is%20currently%20set%20to%20be%20on%20the%20ballot%20solely%20for%20his%20state%20Assembly%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20California%20state%20law%20does%20not%20allow%20for%20candidates%20to%20appear%20on%20the%20same%20ballot%20for%20two%20different%20contests%2C%20which%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Shirley%20Weber's%20office%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sos.ca.gov%2Fadministration%2Fnews-releases-and-advisories%2F2023-news-releases-and-advisories%2Fsecretary-state-announces-determination-californias-20th-congressional-district%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BState%20law%20prohibits%20any%20candidate%20from%20filing%20nomination%20papers%20for%20more%20than%20one%20office%20at%20the%20same%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20office%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20such%2C%20the%20Secretary%20of%20State's%20office%20has%20determined%20that%20Mr.%20Fong's%20filed%20nomination%20papers%20for%20Congressional%20District%2020%20were%20improperly%20submitted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Fong%20will%20not%20appear%20on%20the%20list%20of%20certified%20candidates%20for%20Congressional%20District%2020%20that%20our%20office%20will%20transmit%20to%20county%20election%20officials%20on%20candidates%20on%20December%2028%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20office%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFong%2C%20who%20has%20compiled%20a%20conservative%20record%20in%20the%20California%20Assembly%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20he%20would%20challenge%20the%20Secretary%20of%20State's%20determination%20%26quot%3Bimminently%26quot%3B%20and%20charged%20that%20it%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%20interference%20in%20the%20candidate%20filing%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAssemblyman%20Fong%20has%20qualified%20for%20the%20ballot%20and%20the%20voters%20of%20the%2020th%20Congressional%20District%20deserve%20the%20opportunity%20to%20select%20the%20candidate%20of%20their%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECandidates%20set%20to%20appear%20on%20the%20upcoming%20congressional%20ballot%20include%20Tulare%20County%20Sheriff%20Mike%20Boudreaux%2C%20businessman%20David%20Giglio%2C%20public%20school%20teacher%20Marisa%20Wood%2C%20and%20security%20officer%20Andy%20Morales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-mccarthy-vince-fong-house-special-election-california-ballot-gop-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702757045000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657df7497a3c8094d5ddd40e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fww