20report%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20soldiers%20training%20Donetsk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cda4d020f1cf0019cb3925%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20soldiers%20train%20with%20live%20ammunition%20near%20the%20front%20lines%20in%20Donetsk%20Oblast%20on%20July%2031%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EWojciech%20Grzedzinski%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERussia%20plans%20to%20occupy%20large%20swaths%20of%20Ukrainian%20territory%20by%202026%2C%20Bild%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERussia%20illegally%20annexed%20four%20Ukrainian%20oblasts%20after%20invading%20Ukraine%20in%20February%202022.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20plan%20partly%20relies%20on%20Western%20support%20for%20Kyiv%20waning.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bild.de%2Fbild-plus%2Fpolitik%2Fausland%2Fpolitik-ausland%2Fmehr-land-das-ist-putins-kriegsplan-fuer-die-naechsten-drei-jahre-86419892.bild.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enew%20plan%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20involves%20occupying%20large%20expanses%20of%20territory%20between%202024%20and%202026%2C%20German%20outlet%20Bild%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202022%2C%20Russia%20annexed%20parts%20of%20Donetsk%2C%20Kherson%2C%20Luhansk%2C%20and%20Zaporizhzhia%20oblasts%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20in%20a%20move%20not%20recognized%20by%20the%20international%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20new%20plan%2C%20Russia%20plans%20to%20occupy%20the%20entirety%20of%20Donetsk%20and%20Luhansk%20oblasts%2C%20and%20to%20advance%20to%20the%20Oskil%20River%20in%20Kharkiv%20oblast%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20Bild%20reported%2C%20citing%20unspecified%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20step%20of%20the%20plan%2C%20over%202025%20and%202026%2C%20will%20be%20to%20take%20over%20large%20parts%20of%20the%20Zaporizhzhia%2C%20Dnipro%2C%20and%20Kharkiv%20region%2C%20Bild%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20Bild%20report%2C%20the%20think%20tank%20the%20Institute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.understandingwar.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Frussian-offensive-campaign-assessment-december-15-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BISW%20cannot%20independently%20authenticate%20BILD's%20reporting%2C%20but%20Russia's%20reported%20plans%20for%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20through%202026%20are%20in%20line%20with%20continued%20Russian%20preparations%20for%20a%20prolonged%20war%20effort.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20south%20of%20Ukraine%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20priority%20for%20Russia%2C%20despite%20the%20Kherson%20region%20having%20been%20occupied%20in%20the%20first%20year%20of%20the%20war%2C%20and%20Russia%20now%20only%20wants%20to%20stop%20Ukrainian%20forces%20from%20advancing%20towards%20Crimea%2C%20the%20intelligence%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBild%20said%20a%20source%20with%20inside%20information%20told%20the%20publication%20that%20Russia%20planned%20to%20occupy%20the%20entire%20eastern%20areas%20to%20the%20left%20of%20the%20Dnipro%20River%20within%2036%20months.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20river%20is%20then%20the%20new%20front%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%2C%20per%20Bild.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20river%20has%20become%20the%20center%20of%20the%20war%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20with%20Ukraine%20conducting%20counteroffensive%20operations%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-expandingbridgehead-along-the-dnipro-river-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eestablishing%20a%20bridgehead%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20eastern%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20preparations%2C%20such%20as%20its%20growing%20defense%20budget%2C%20also%20suggest%20that%20it