0Scotland%2C%20and%20the%20beginnings%20of%20his%20romance%20with%20his%20future%20wife%2C%20Kate%20Middleton.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20episodes%20take%20on%20a%20sort%20of%20rom-com%20narrative%20as%2C%20despite%20fancying%20each%20other%20very%20much%2C%20Kate%20and%20Wills%20can't%20get%20their%20timings%20quite%20right%20and%20whenever%20one%20is%20ready%20to%20make%20a%20move%2C%20the%20other%20is%20dating%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%26quot%3BThe%20Crown%2C%26quot%3B%20Prince%20William%20(Ed%20McVey)%20is%20shown%20to%20initially%20have%20some%20trouble%20getting%20to%20know%20girls%20at%20university.%20It's%20only%20after%20his%20younger%20brother%20Harry's%20(Luther%20Ford)%20encouragement%20that%20he%20makes%20a%20move%20on%20a%20girl%20at%20a%20house%20party%20and%20they%20begin%20dating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222502%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prince%20William%20is%20shown%20to%20be%20dating%20a%20student%20named%20Lola%20(Honor%20Swinton%20Byrne).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657dda6450edbc52a8650e14%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221251%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPrince%20William%20(Ed%20McVey)%20is%20shown%20to%20be%20dating%20a%20student%20named%20Lola%20(Honor%20Swinton%20Byrne).%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20show%2C%20the%20fictional%20character%20Lola%20Airedale-Cavendish-Kinkade%20(Honor%20Swinton%20Byrne)%20and%20William's%20romance%20quickly%20fizzled%20out%20when%20she%20realized%20that%20William%20was%20%26quot%3Bbracing%20and%20outdoorsy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20real%20life%2C%20Prince%20William%20reportedly%20had%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3Eseveral%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cstrong%3Egirlfriends%20before%20Kate%20Middleton%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20real%20life%2C%20William%20reportedly%20had%20several%20girlfriends%20at%20university%20before%20he%20began%20dating%20Kate%20(and%20a%20few%20more%20before%20he