led%20position%20and%20mind%20to%20commit%20murder%20of%20people%20belonging%20to%20a%20specific%20community%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20court%20said%20while%20rejecting%20his%20bail%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaudhary%2C%20who%20is%20lodged%20in%20a%20jail%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Akola%2C%20about%20550%20kms%20from%20here%2C%20was%20present%20in%20the%20court%20during%20the%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20bail%20plea%2C%20filed%20last%20month%20through%20advocates%20Amit%20Mishra%20and%20Pankaj%20Ghildiyal%2C%20the%20accused%20said%20he%20has%20been%20suffering%20from%20%26quot%3Bhaunted%20illusions%20of%20the%20ghostly%20world%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20doing%20some%20weird%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20opposed%20his%20plea%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20appeared%20to%20have%20harboured%20%26quot%3Banger%20and%20grudge%26quot%3B%20towards%20a%20particular%20community%20and%20showed%20no%20remorse%20for%20the%20crime%20committed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20his%20bail%20is%20granted%2C%20it%20could%20create%20a%20negative%20image%20about%20the%20law%20and%20also%20create%20fear%2C%20panic%20and%20insecurity%20among%20certain%20religious%20groups%2C%20the%20Government%20Railway%20Police%20(RPF)%2C%20which%20is%20probing%20the%20case%2C%20had%20submitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUmesa%20Khatoon%2C%20wife%20of%20victim%20Asgar%20Shaikh%2C%20through%20her%20advocates%20Karim%20Pathan%20and%20Fazlurrahman%20Shaikh%2C%20had%20also%20opposed%20Chaudhary's%20bail%2C%20saying%20the%20accused%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%20minded%20person%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Ba%20threat%20to%20national%20security%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20prima%20facie%20case%20of%20four%20brutal%20murders%20committed%20by%20the%20hatemonger%20accused%20witnessed%20by%2039%20eyewitnesses%20and%20virtually%20witnessed%20by%20the%20entire%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20advocates%20submitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20July%2031%20on%20board%