t%20By%20Lover's%20Car%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20Thane%20incident%2C%20wherein%20a%20woman%20was%20allegedly%20run%20over%20by%20her%20boyfriend's%20car%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20road%2C%20Maharashtra%20Minister%20Sudhir%20Mungantiwar%20said%20that%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20matter%20will%20have%20to%20face%20the%20whip%20of%20law%20even%20if%20he%20is%20the%20son%20of%20an%20officer%20or%20a%20big%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20ANI%20on%20the%20incident%20in%20Chandrapur%2C%20Mungantiwar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhether%20it%20is%20an%20officer's%20son%20or%20some%20big%20leader's%20son%2C%20he%20will%20have%20to%20bear%20the%20whip%20of%20the%20law%20and%20Constitution.%20No%20matter%20who%20it%20is%2C%20if%20they%20have%20committed%20this%20crime%2C%20then%20they%20would%20be%20punished.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20also%20reacted%20to%20the%20case%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20incident%20not%20only%20brings%20goosebumps%20to%20a%20person%20but%20also%20exposes%20many%20people%20who%20are%20in%20authority.%20The%20accused%2C%20who%20has%20committed%20the%20heinous%20crime%2C%20is%20the%20President%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20Yuva%20Morcha%20and%20his%20father%20is%20a%20very%20senior%20bureaucrat%20in%20Thane%20district.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20talks%20about%20women's%20safety%20but%20it%20is%20actually%20the%20work%20that%20is%20done%20that%20really%20matters%20and%20that%20kind%20of%20work%20for%20women%20is%20not%20seen%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%26quot%3B%20Chaturvedi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20very%20unfortunate%20incident%20and%20I%20want%20to%20question%20the%20BJP%20about%20how%20the%20party%20could%20place%20responsibilities%20on%20such%20people%20who%20are%20so%20%26quot%3BMahila%20Virodhi%2C%26quot%3B%20asserted%20Chaturvedi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoes%20the%20Mahila%20Bachao-Mahila%20Badhao%20programme%20of%20the%20BJP%20give%20this%20message%20when%20there%20are%20incidents%20such%20as%20the%20women's%20protest%20or%20this%20recent%20Thane%20incident%3F%20she%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leader%20Narayan%20Rane%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%20the%20opposition%20is%20saying%20that%20law%20and%20order%20has%20deteriorated%20in%20Maharashtra.%20My%20question%20is%20that%20both%20Disha%20Salian%20and%20Sushant%20Singh%20were%20murdered%20during%20their%20time%2C%20was%20there%20law%20and%20order%20at%20that%20time%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20when%20a%20woman%20is%20run%20over%20by%20a%20vehicle%2C%20then%20it%20is%20wrong%20to%20say%20that%20law%20and%20order%20are%20not%20good.%20They%20have%20no%20other%20topic.%20Our%20government%20is%20doing%20good%20work%20in%20Maharashtra.%20If%20a%20case%20is%20registered%2C%20he%20will%20be%20arrested.%20After%20an%20investigation%2C%20the%20police%20will%20arrest%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Rane%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Tariq%20Anwar%20also%20condemned%20the%20incident%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20sad%20that%20in%20our%20society%2C%20the%20way%20of%20thinking%20has%20still%20not%20changed%2C%20especially%20in%20cases%20like%20this%2C%20where%20love%20is%20involved.%20Many%20children%20commit%20suicide%2C%20murder%2C%20and%20other%20such%20crimes%20in%20matters%20like%20these.%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20this%20is%20a%20social%20evil%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20cured.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2026-year-old%20woman%20was%20severely%20injured%20when%20her%20boyfriend%2C%20who%20is%20the%20son%20of%20a%20senior%20bureaucrat%2C%20allegedly%20tried%20to%20run%20her%20over%20with%20his%20car%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Thane%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Ashwajit%20Gaikwad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20ANI%20on%20the%20incident%2C%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(DCP)%20Amar%20Singh%20Jadhav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20incident%20took%20place%20around%204%20a.m.%20on%20Monday%20near%20a%20hotel%20on%20Ghodbunder%20Road%2C%20where%20the%20woman%20had%20gone%20to%20meet%20Ashwajit%20Gaikwad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20argument%20broke%20out%20between%20the%20victim%2C%20Ashwajeet%20Gaikwad%20and%20two%20other%20persons%20identified%20as%20Romil%20Patil%20and%20Sagar.%20The%20victim%20suffered%20injuries%20after%20the%20argument%2C%20and%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20where%20the%20police%20recorded%20her%20statement.%20According%20to%20that%2C%20further%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20and%20a%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20three%20accused%20under%20relevant%20sections%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20under%20IPC%20sections%20279%20(rash%20driving%20or%20riding%20on%20a%20public%20way)%2C%20338%20(causing%20grievous%20hurt%20by%20an%20act%20endangering%20the%20life%20or%20personal%20safety%20of%20others)%2C%20323%20(punishment%20for%20voluntarily%20causing%20hurt)%2C%20504%20(intentional%20insult%20with%20intent%20to%20provoke%20breach%20of%20the%20peace)%2C%20and%2034%20(acts%20done%20by%20several%20persons%20in%20furtherance%20of%20common%20intention)%20(against%20accused%20Ashwajeet%20Gaikwad%2C%20Romil%20Patil%20and%20Sagar).%20Further%20investigation%20is%20being%20done%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20victim's%20statement%2C%26quot%3B%20informed%20the%20DCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%20shared%20details%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThree%20bones%20in%20my%20right%20leg%20are%20broken.%20It%20has%20been%20operated%20on.%20From%20my%20left%20shoulder%20to%20my%20hips%2C%20I've%20had%20deep%20injuries.%20I%20cannot%20move%20my%20body.%20Four%20days%20ago%2C%20I%20went%20to%20file%20an%20FIR--the%20day%20all%20this%20happened.%20But%20no%20action%20was%20taken.%20Today%2C%20when%20I%20posted%20on%20social%20media%2C%20the%20police%20supported%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20early%20on%20Monday%20morning%20near%20a%20hotel%20in%20Thane%20and%20police%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20the%20accused%2C%20Ashwajit%20Gaikwad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20her%20information%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20victim%20Priya%20Singh's%20lawyer%2C%20Darshana%20Pawar%2C%20told%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20met%20Priya%20in%20the%20morning.%20She%20is%20stable%20but%20the%20injuries%20are%20quite%20severe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20per%20the%20injuries%2C%20307%20(of%20IPC)%20should%20have%20been%20recorded%2C%20which%20has%20not%20been%20recorded.%20We%20have%20been%20requesting%20the%20investigating%20officers%20and%20police%20officers%20to%20take%20307%20and%20356%20on%20record.%20But%2C%20to%20date%2C%20they%20have%20not%20taken%20it.%20It's%20been%20more%20than%20four%20days.%20If%20they%20don't%20proceed%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20approach%20the%20High%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20the%20lawyer%20for%20the%20victim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20details%20on%20the%20matter%20are%20awaited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702752360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-08%2Fd64idvc8_sudhir-mungantiwar-650_625x300_14_August_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhether-it-is-an-officers-son-minister-on-woman-hit-by-lovers-car-4687298%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reacting%20to%20the%20Thane%20incident%2C%20wherein%20a%20woman%20was%20allegedly%20run%20over%20by%20her%20boyfriend's%20car%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20road%2C%20Maharashtra%20Minister%20Sudhir%20Mungantiwar%20said%20that%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20matter%20will%20have%20to%20face%20the%20whip%20of%20law.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22