0opens%20fire.%20He%20declares%20that%20they're%20terrorists.%20They%20(the%20Israeli%20forces)%20open%20fire.%20Two%20(hostages)%20are%20killed%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20told%20reporters%2C%20per%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20victims%20were%20identified%20as%20Yotam%20Haim%20and%20Alon%20Shamriz%20who%20were%20taken%20from%20Kibbutz%20Kfar%20Aza%20during%20Hamas'%20October%207%20attacks%2C%20and%20Samer%20Al-Talalka%2C%20who%20had%20been%20abducted%20from%20Kibbutz%20Nir%20Am.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idf.il%2Fen%2Fmini-sites%2Fidf-press-releases-regarding-the-hamas-israel-war%2Fdecember-pr%2Fduring-combat-in-shejaiya-the-idf-mistakenly-identified-3-israeli-hostages-as-a-threat-and-fired-toward-them-as-a-result-they-were-killed%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAlon%2520Shamriz%252C%2520was%2520kidnapped%2520from%2Cthe%2520families%2520its%2520heartfelt%2520condolences.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20addressing%20the%20news%2C%20the%20IDF%20said%20it%20expressed%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20remorse%20over%20the%20incident%20and%20sends%20the%20families%20its%20heartfelt%20condolences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAl-Talalka%2C%2025%2C%20was%20mourned%20by%20around%20300%20people%20at%20his%20funeral%20in%20Hura%2C%20southern%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlaa%20Al-Talalka%2C%20a%20cousin%20of%20his%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20going%20to%20start%20pointing%20fingers%2C%20who%20is%20guilty%20and%20who%20is%20not.%20It%20is%20just%20not%20the%20time.%20The%20families%20are%20thinking%20only%20of%20how%20to%20bring%20the%20hostages%20back%20alive.%20This%20is%20the%20time%20to%20ask%20for%20the%20war%20to%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20100%20hostages%20are%20still%20in%20Gaza%2C%20with%20Israeli%20calls%20for%20Red%20Cross%20access%20going%20unheeded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERuby%20Chen%2C%20the%20father%20of%20a%20captive%2C%20expressed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjonathan-pollard-says-hostages-families-should-have-been-jailed%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euncertainty%20families%20faced%20each%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20likening%20it%20to%20%26quot%3BRussian%20roulette.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIsrael's%20government%20needs%20to%20get%20a%20grip%20and%20bring%20back%20the%20hostages%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20Hamas%20released%20more%20than%20100%20hostages%20following%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-hostages-killed-idf-holding-white-flag-says-military-official%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702751926000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657dbd6b7a3c8094d5ddd0b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-hostages-killed-idf-holding-white-flag-says-military-official%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20killings%20happened%20in%20Shejaiya%2C%20a%20war-torn%20area%20in%20Gaza%20City%20where%20Hamas%20militants%20often%20attempt%20to%20blend%20in%20with%20civilians%2C%20the%20official%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Rommen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A109%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-hostages-killed-idf-holding-white-flag-says-military-official%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHis%20Agony%20Reached%20Me%26quot%3B%3A%20Smriti%20Irani%20On%20Speaker's%20Letter%20To%20MPs%20Over%20Breach%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20all%20Members%20of%20Parliament%2C%20emphasizing%20that%20there%20is%20no%20correlation%20between%20the%20security%20breach%20and%20the%20recent%20suspension%20of%2013%20MPs%20from%20the%20Lower%20House%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20prioritizing%20Parliament's%20security%20and%20proper%20conduct%20during%20proceedings%2C%20regardless%20of%20political%20affiliations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20a%20similar%20thought%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20highlighted%20the%20responsibility%20of%20MPs%20to%20uphold%20Parliament's%20dignity%20and%20expressed%20concern%20about%20indiscipline%20being%20given%20political%20colours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2013%20MPs%20were%20suspended%20from%20Parliament%20on%20Thursday%20%26quot%3Bfor%20creating%20a%20ruckus%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20House%20over%20their%20demand%20for%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20breach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%2013%20MPs%20suspended%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20nine%20are%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20two%20from%20the%20CPM%2C%20one%20from%20the%20CPI%2C%20and%20one%20from%20the%20DMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20following%20the%20security%20breach%20in%20the%20Parliament%2C%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%2C%20in%20his%20letter%2C%20said%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bunfortunate%26quot%3B%20that%20some%20members%20and%20political%20parties%20are%20linking%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20House%20to%20suspend%20some%20members%20to%20the%20Parliament%20security%20lapse%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20unwarranted.%20There%20is%20no%20association%20between%20the%20suspension%20of%20honourable%20members%20and%20the%20incident%20which%20took%20place%20on%20December%2013%2C%202023.%20The%20suspension%20of%20honourable%20members%20is%20purely%20to%20uphold%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20house%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20letter%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20well%20aware%20that%20the%20people%20of%20our%20country%20do%20not%20appreciate%20the%20inappropriate%20conduct%20and%20interruptions%20during%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20House.%20That%20is%20the%20reason%20we%20are%20unanimous%20that%20we%20would%20establish%20highest%20standards%20of%20parliamentary%20decorum%20and%20dignity%2C%26quot%3B%20Om%20Birla%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bcompelled%20to%20take%20strict%20action%20of%20suspending%20members%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20time%20of%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20building%20of%20our%20Parliament%2C%20we%20had%20resolved%20that%20we%20will%20refrain%20from%20bringing%20placards%20inside%20the%20House%3B%20we%20will%20not%20create%20ruckus%20in%20the%20well%20of%20the%20House%2C%26quot%3B%20Birla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20also%20stated%20that%20a%20high-level%20committee%20has%20been%20constituted%20to%20inquire%20into%20the%20security%20lapse%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20high-level%20committee%20has%20been%20constituted%20for%20an%20in-depth%20investigation%20of%20the%20incident%20that%20took%20place%20inside%20the%20House.%20The%20committee%20has%20started%20working.%20The%20report%20of%20this%20committee%20will%20soon%20be%20shared%20with%20the%20House%26quot%3B%2C%20read%20the%20letter.%26quot%3BIn%20addition%2C%20I%20have%20also%20constituted%20a%20high-powered%20committee%20which%20will%20review%20various%20aspects%20of%20security%20in%20the%20parliament%20complex%20and%20formulate%20a%20concrete%20action%20plan%20to%20ensure%20such%20incidents%20do%20not%20occur%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20which%20party%20we%20belong%20to%2C%20we%20all%20should%20contemplate%20the%20security%20of%20the%20parliament%20and%20ensure%20that%20the%20proceedings%20are%20carried%20out%20properly.%20Such%20incidents%20have%20happened%20in%20the%20past%20too%2C%20while%20the%20opposition%20was%20in%20power.%20But%20those%20issues%20were%20not%20politicized%2C%20rather%20proper%20enquiries%20were%20made%20into%20these%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20link%20between%20the%20suspension%20of%20the%20MPs%20and%20the%20security%20breach%20incident.%20They%20were%20suspended%20for%20creating%20a%20ruckus%20inside%20the%20House.%20There%20is%20a%20certain%20way%20to%20revolt%20against%20an%20issue.%20But%20holding%20placards%20and%20not%20letting%20the%20House%20function%20is%20unfair.%20I%20condemn%20such%20behaviour%26quot%3B%2C%20Goyal%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmriti%20Irani%20said%20that%20the%20MPs%20were%20suspended%20as%20they%20%26quot%3Bshredded%26quot%3B%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThrough%20the%20letter%2C%20the%20Speaker's%20agony%20and%20concern%20reached%20me...Even%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20Speaker%20invited%20all%20political%20parties%20for%20their%20suggestions%20regarding%20security%20and%20proceedings%20of%20the%20House...As%20MPs%2C%20it%20is%20our%20responsibility%20to%20see%20that%20we%20do%20not%20hurt%20the%20dignity%20of%20Parliament.%20Speaker%20does%20not%20belong%20to%20one%20side%20but%20the%20entire%20country%20and%20serves%20the%20House%20as%20the%20custodian%20of%20the%20Constitution's%20dignity.%20His%20letter%20also%20reflected%20the%20pain%20that%20some%20MPs%20were%20suspended%20as%20they%20shredded%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20House%20but%20the%20act%20against%20indiscipline%20is%20being%20given%20political%20colours%26quot%3B%2C%20Smriti%20Irani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2013%2C%20two%20men%20jumped%20inside%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20the%20visitor's%20gallery%20above%20the%20chamber%20and%20threw%20smoke%20cannisters%20inside%20the%20Parliament%2C%20triggering%20panic%20on%20the%20day%20India%20marked%20the%2022nd%20anniversary%20of%20the%202001%20Parliament%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20breach%20happened%20on%20the%20anniversary%20of%20the%202001%20Parliament%20terror%20attack.%20Two%20people--Sagar%20Sharma%20and%20Manoranjan%20D--jumped%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber%20from%20the%20public%20gallery%20during%20Zero%20Hour%2C%20released%20yellow%20gas%20from%20canisters%20and%20shouted%20anti-establishment%20slogans%20before%20being%20overpowered%20by%20the%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20it%2C%20in%20another%20incident%2C%20two%20protestors%20--%20Neelam%20(42)%20and%20Amol%20(25)%20--%20protested%20outside%20the%20Parliament%20with%20similar%20gas%20canisters.%20However%2C%20all%20four%20were%20sent%20to%20seven-day%20custody%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20Special%20Cell%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fifth%20accused%20Lalit%20Jha%2C%20who%20allegedly%20planned%20the%20incident%2C%20has%20also%20been%20arrested%20and%20Mahesh%20Kumawat%20is%20the%20sixth%20accused%20arrested%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20on%20Saturday%20informed%20the%20Patiala%20House%20Court%20that%20the%20Parliament%20Security%20breach%20conspiracy%20had%20been%20going%20on%20since%20more%20than%20last%20year%2C%20and%20freshly%20arrested%20accused%20Mahesh%20attended%20all%20the%20meetings%20held%20in%20different%20cities%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Public%20Prosecutor%20Advocate%20Akhand%20Pratap%20Singh%2C%20who%20appeared%20for%20the%20Special%20Cell%20of%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20further%20informed%20the%20court%20that%20Mahesh%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20other%20accused%20for%20the%20last%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20further%20claimed%20that%20he%20(Mahesh)%20alongwith%20others%20wanted%20to%20create%20anarchy%20in%20the%20country%20so%20that%20they%20could%20compel%20the%20government%20to%20meet%20their%20unjust%20and%20illegal%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20opposition%20MPs%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20have%20been%20demanding%20a%20word%20from%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20over%20the%20security%20lapse%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20reiterated%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20statement%20from%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20over%20the%20massive%20security%20breach%2C%20the%20Congress%20President%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20let%20the%20House%20function.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20serious%20issue%20and%20the%20government%20should%20pay%20attention%20to%20it.%20We%20are%20repeatedly%20saying%20in%20Parliament%20that%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20should%20come%20to%20the%20House%20and%20give%20a%20statement%20but%20he%20does%20not%20want%20to%20come.%20They%20(BJP)%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20let%20the%20House%20function.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20good%20thing%20for%20democracy%20but%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20talking%20to%20people%20who%20do%20not%20believe%20in%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20Kharge%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20allegations%20against%20the%20opposition%20for%20playing%20politics%20over%20the%20incident%2C%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20BJP's%20job%20is%20to%20abuse%20the%20Congress%20and%20get%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(BJP)%20seek%20votes%20by%20taking%20the%20name%20of%20Congress.%20They%20abuse%20Nehru%20ji%20and%20Gandhi%20ji%20to%20get%20votes.%20Their%20job%20is%20to%20abuse%20us%20and%20get%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20firing%20a%20fresh%20salvo%20at%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20over%20the%20massive%20security%20breach%20in%20Parliament%2C%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20KC%20Venugopal%20on%20Saturday%20said%20it%20wasn't%20the%20opposition%20members%20but%20Delhi%20Police%20that%20politicised%20the%20incident%20after%20labelling%20it%20as%20a%20terror%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelhi%20Police%20called%20it%20(parliament%20security%20breach)%20a%20terror%20attack.%20It%20comes%20under%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%2C%20doesn't%20it%3F%20We%20(O