nt%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Birla%20said%2013%20opposition%20members%20have%20been%20suspended%20from%20the%20House%20%26quot%3Bpurely%20to%20uphold%26quot%3B%20its%20sanctity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20time%20of%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20building%20of%20our%20Parliament%2C%20we%20had%20resolved%20that%20we%20will%20refrain%20from%20bringing%20placards%20inside%20the%20House%3B%20we%20will%20not%20create%20ruckus%20in%20the%20Well%20of%20the%20House%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20indeed%20unfortunate%20that%20some%20members%20and%20political%20parties%20are%20linking%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20House%20to%20suspend%20these%20members%20to%20the%20security%20breach%20when%20two%20persons%20had%20jumped%20into%20the%20MPs'%20chamber%20from%20the%20visitors'%20gallery%20on%20December%2013%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20have%20slammed%20the%20suspension%2C%20noting%20that%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20BJP%20MP%20Prathap%20Simha%2C%20who%20facilitated%20the%20passes%20of%20two%20accused%20who%20carried%20smoke%20cannisters%20with%20them%2C%20while%20their%20members%20have%20been%20suspended%20for%20raising%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20unwarranted.%20There%20is%20no%20association%20between%20the%20suspension%20of%20Hon'ble%20members%20and%20the%20incident%20which%20took%20place%20on%20December%2013%2C%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20speaker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Birla%20noted%20that%20he%20had%20discussed%20the%20security%20issue%20with%20leaders%20of%20all%20parties%20on%20the%20same%20day%20and%20added%20that%20some%20of%20the%20important%20suggestions%20made%20during%20the%20meeting%20were%20implemented%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20message%20to%20the%20opposition%2C%20he%20said%20incidents%20such%20as%20visitors%20carrying%20pistols%2C%20shouting%20slogans%2C%20jumping%20from%20the%20visitors'%20gallery%20and%20throwing%20leaflets%20have%20occurred%20in%20the%20past%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nation%20has%20also%20witnessed%20an%20incident%20when%20some%20members%20carried%20pepper%20spray%20inside%20the%20House%2C%20he%20said%20in%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20chaotic%20scenes%20witnessed%20during%20the%20process%20to%20divide%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20to%20form%20the%20separate%20state%20of%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20all%20such%20incidents%2C%20the%20House%20displayed%20exemplary%20solidarity%20and%20expressed%20its%20collective%20resolve%20against%20such%20incidents%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20speaker%20said%20people%20of%20the%20country%20do%20not%20appreciate%20the%20inappropriate%20conduct%20and%20interruptions%20during%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20House.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20in%20this%20context%20that%20the%20House%20was%20compelled%20to%20take%20strict%20action%20of%20suspending%20Hon'ble%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20opposition%20looks%20to%20intensify%20its%20protests%2C%20Mr%20Birla%20urged%20all%20members%20to%20faithfully%20discharge%20their%20duties%20towards%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficial%20sources%20noted%20that%20numerous%20incidents%20of%20violation%20of%20security%20norms%20have%20happened%20in%20the%20past%2C%20including%20three%20cases%20of%20visitors%20jumping%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber%20between%201991-94.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20a%20dozen%20cases%20of%20people%20shouting%20slogans%20and%20throwing%20leaflets%20from%20the%20visitors'%20galleries%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201983%2C%20a%20visitor%20shouted%20slogans%20and%20threw%20a%20slipper%20into%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs'%20chamber.%20There%20are%20at%20least%20six%20instances%20of%20visitors%20shouting%20slogans%20and%20throwing%20pamphlets%20in%20the%20Upper%20House%20of%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headlin