A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67738792%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67738792.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67738792.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kamal%20Nath%20Out%2C%20OBC%20Leader%20Jitu%20Patwari%20New%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20its%20drubbing%20in%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20replaced%20senior%20leader%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Kamal%20Nath%20as%20the%20state%20unit%20chief%20with%20other%20backward%20class%20(OBC)%20leader%20Jitu%20Patwari.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOBCs%20account%20for%20over%2050%25%20of%20voters%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20selection%20of%20Mr%20Patwari%20-%20who%20lost%20to%20a%20BJP%20candidate%20from%20the%20Rau%20Assembly%20seat%20with%20a%20margin%20of%20over%2035%2C000%20votes%20-%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20the%20party's%20attempt%20to%20make%20a%20fresh%20start%20in%20the%20crucial%20heartland%20state%20ahead%20of%20the%20all-important%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20which%20are%20less%20than%20four%20months%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Mr%20Patwari's%20appointment%2C%20speculation%20is%20rife%20about%20the%20political%20future%20of%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20who%20is%20now%2077%20years%20old%20and%20has%20been%20a%20Union%20Cabinet%20minister%2C%20nine-time%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20for%20about%2015%20months.%C2%A0He%20was%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20for%20over%20five%20years%20and%20had%20to%20resign%20as%20chief%20minister%20in%202020%20after%20the%20rebellion%20by%20senior%20leader%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20year's%20elections%2C%20which%20were%20held%20on%20November%2017%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20managed%20to%20secure%20only%2066%20seats%20in%20the%20230-member%20Assembly%20and%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%20163%20despite%20being%20in%20power%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20loss%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20decided%20to%20retain%20Deepak%20Baij%20as%20the%20state%20unit%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20Math%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20party%20has%20also%20appointed%20Umang%20Singhar%20as%20the%20Congress%20Legislative%20Party%20leader%2C%20which%20means%20that%20he%20will%20be%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20and%20has%20picked%20Hemant%20Katare%20as%20the%20deputy%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20picks%20are%20significant%20as%2C%20apart%20from%20effecting%20a%20generational%20change%2C%20they%20also%20reflect%20the%20Congress'%20attempt%20at%20caste%20balancing.%20Kamal%20Nath%20is%20a%20Brahmin%20leader%20and%20has%20now%20been%20replaced%20with%20an%20OBC%20leader%20in%20Jitu%20Patwari.%20Umang%20Singhar%20is%20a%20tribal%20and%20the%20nephew%20of%20late%20Jamuna%20Devi%2C%20who%20was%20a%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20and%20represented%20the%20state%20both%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20naming%20of%20Hemant%20Katare%20may%20have%20been%20done%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20retaining%20the%20votes%20of%20the%20Brahmin%20community%20after%20replacing%20Kamal%20Nath.%20Katare%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bgiant%20killer%26quot%3B%20after%20defeating%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20cooperatives%20minister%20Arvind%20Singh%20Bhadoria%20of%20the%20BJP%20by%20over%2069%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20appointments%2C%20a%20Congress%20statement%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20president%20has%20appointed%20Shri%20Jitu%20Patwari%20as%20the%20president%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%2C%20with%20immediate%20effect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20party%20appreciates%20the%20contributions%20of%20outgoing%20PCC%20president%2C%20Shri%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChhattisgarh%20Chief%20Retained%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20could%20not%20retain%20power%20and%20got%2035%20seats%20against%20the%20BJP's%2054%20in%20the%2090-member%20assembly%2C%20the%20party%20has%20decided%20to%20continue%20with%20Deepak%20Baij%20as%20the%20state%20unit%20chief.%20It%20has%20appointed%20former%20Chhattisgarh%20Assembly%20Speaker%20Charan%20Das%20Mahant%20as%20the%20Congress%20Legislative%20Party%20leader.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mahant%20is%20an%20OBC%20leader%20and%20had%20retained%20the%20Sakti%20seat%20by%20defeating%20BJP's%20Khilawan%20Sahu%20with%20a%20margin%20of%20over%2012%2C000%20votes%20in%20this%20year's%20elections%2C%20which%20were%20held%20in%20two%20phases%2C%20on%20November%207%20and%2017.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702747140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-02%2Fvlp4t74g_kamal-nath_625x300_21_February_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkamal-nath-replaced-jitu-patwari-is-new-madhya-pradesh-congress-chief-4686304%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Days%20after%20its%20drubbing%20in%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20replaced%20senior%20leader%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Kamal%20Nath%20as%20the%20state%20unit%20chief%20with%20Jitu%20Patwari.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkamal-nath-replaced-jitu-patwari-is-new-madhya-pradesh-congress-chief-4686304%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkamal-nath-replaced-jitu-patwari-is-new-madhya-pradesh-congress-chief-4686304%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%