ct%20that%20no%20person%2C%20individual%2C%20groups%2C%20associations%2C%20political%20parties%2C%20or%20the%20like%20shall%20visit%20the%20place%20of%20the%20victim%20except%20with%20the%20prior%20written%20permission%20of%20the%20medical%20officer%20in-charge%20of%20the%20hospital%20or%20the%20doctor%20treating%20the%20victim%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20urgent%20hearing%20in%20the%20judge's%20chamber%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20issued%20the%20order%20after%20noticing%20a%20news%20report%20on%20television%20that%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Belagavi%20incident%20victim%20is%20to%20be%20visited%20by%20the%20representatives%20of%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20as%20well%20as%20by%20the%20delegation%20of%20a%20political%20party.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20the%20HC%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20order%20shall%20not%20prevent%20the%20family%20members%20of%20the%20victim%2C%20the%20official%20representatives%20of%20Statutory%20Authorities%2F%20Commissions%20or%20the%20Investigating%20Agencies%20to%20visit%20the%20victim%20in%20a%20need%20based%20manner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20on%20December%2012%2C%20on%20its%20own%20took%20cognisance%20of%20the%20news%20of%20the%20incident%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Hukkeri%20Taluk%20in%20Belagavi%20District.%20While%20hearing%20the%20petition%20on%20December%2014%2C%20it%20had%20directed%20the%20personal%20presence%20of%20the%20Belagavi%20Commissioner%20in%20the%20Court%20on%20December%2018%20to%20file%20an%20additional%20report%20on%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20incident.%20The%20court%20had%20ordered%20that%20the%20offenders%20should%20be%20arrested%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702742460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-02%