re%20irrelevant.%20Her%20witty%2C%20funny%20answer%20has%20left%20some%20netizens%20offended...%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fnetizens-are-offended-with-twinkle-khannas-comment-as-she-calls-men-desert-she-gives-a-befitting-reply%2Farticleshow%2F106050651.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dharavi%20Tender%20Terms%20Finalised%20Under%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20Regime%3A%20Adani%20Group%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20for%20the%20redevelopment%20of%20Dharavi%20slum%20in%20Mumbai%20was%20awarded%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group%20through%20a%20fair%2C%20open%2C%20and%20internationally%20competitive%20bidding%20process%2C%20and%20the%20tender%20conditions%20were%20finalised%20when%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20government%20was%20in%20power%2C%20as%20per%20a%20release%20issued%20by%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20a%20concerted%20effort%20is%20being%20made%20to%20disseminate%20misinformation%20about%20certain%20aspects%20of%20the%20project%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20release%20said%20after%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20on%20Saturday%20led%20a%20march%20against%20the%20business%20conglomerate%20which%20was%20awarded%20rights%20to%20redevelop%20Dharavi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20morcha%20was%20taken%20out%20from%20Dharavi%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group%20office%20located%20in%20the%20Bandra%20Kurla%20Complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20government%20in%20July%20formally%20awarded%20the%20259-hectare%20Dharavi%20Redevelopment%20project%20to%20an%20Adani%20Group%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20tender%20conditions%20were%20finalised%20during%20the%20tenure%20of%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20government%2C%20which%20demitted%20office%20at%20the%20end%20of%20June%202022%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20release%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20finalised%20conditions%2C%20including%20the%20obligations%20and%20incentives%2C%20which%20were%20known%20to%20all%20the%20bidders%2C%20have%20not%20been%20changed%20for%20the%20awardee%20post%20the%20tendering%20process.%20Hence%2C%20it%20is%20wrong%20to%20claim%20that%20any%20special%20benefits%20have%20been%20given%20to%20the%20awardee%2C%20the%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20reiterated%20that%20all%20eligible%20tenement%20holders%20will%20be%20provided%20with%20a%20key-to-key%20solution%2C%20which%20means%20they%20will%20move%20into%20their%20new%20homes%20in%20Dharavi%20itself.%20As%20per%20the%20tender%20conditions%2C%20even%20ineligible%20tenement%20holders%20will%20be%20provided%20accommodation%20under%20the%20Rental%20Housing%20Policy%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tender%20provisions%20also%20ensure%20that%20eligible%20residential%20tenements%20will%20receive%2017%25%20more%20area%20than%20other%20SRA%20projects%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20generation%20and%20usage%20of%20TDR%20are%20as%20per%20the%20tender%20conditions%20and%20fully%20compliant%20with%20the%20relevant%20laws.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20resettlement%20of%20Dharavikars%20is%20not%20affected%20by%20Transferable%20Development%20Rights%20(TDR)%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20protesters%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20redevelopment%20project%20involves%20TDR%20irregularities%20worth%20more%20than%20Rs%20100%20crore%2C%20which%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20scam%20in%20the%20world%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20spokesperson%2C%20however%2C%20stated%20that%20the%20TDR%20from%20the%20project%20will%20be%20managed%20and%20monitored%20transparently%20through%20a%20specially%20created%20portal%20by%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Greater%20Mumbai%20(MCGM)%20and%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20government%20has%20entered%20into%20a%2099-year%20lease%20agreement%20with%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20and%20then%20it%20will%20be%20sub-leased%20on%2030%20years%2030%20years%20basis%20like%20any%20other%20government%20land%20in%20Mumbai%20to%20the%20housing%20societies.%20There%20is%20no%20change%20in%20this%20policy%20for%20the%20Dharavi%20Redevelopment%20Project%2C%20the%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20general%20consensus%2C%20not%20only%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20Maharashtra%20but%20also%20across%20the%20whole%20of%20India%2C%20for%20transforming%20Dharavi%20and%20providing%20the%20people%20of%20Dharavi%20with%20better%20living%20conditions%2C%20adequate%20hygiene%2C%20education%20and%20vocational%20training%2C%20healthcare%2C%20employment%20opportunities%2C%20essential%20amenities%20and%20a%20life%20of%20dignity%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dharavi%20project%20assumes%20added%20significance%20because%20many%20earlier%20attempts%20have%20failed%20to%20deliver.%20It%20is%20against%20this%20backdrop%20that%20the%20Adani%20Group%20has%20taken%20up%20the%20challenge%20and%20the%20responsibility%20of%20transforming%20Dharavi%20with%20all%20the%20above%20facilities%2C%20the%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20transformational%20project%20like%20Dharavi%20needs%20support%20from%20all%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20from%20political%20parties%20cutting%20across%20ideologies%20and%20differences%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702739700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvim