position-rally-calling-for-government-to-resign%2Famp_articleshow%2F106050124.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Covid%20Sub-Variant%20JN.1%20Case%20Detected%20In%2079-Year-Old%20Kerala%20Woman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20case%20of%20COVID-19%20sub-variant%20JN.%201%20has%20been%20detected%20in%20Kerala%20as%20part%20of%20an%20ongoing%20routine%20surveillance%20activity%20of%20the%20Indian%20SARS-CoV-2%20Genomics%20Consortium%20(INSACOG)%2C%20a%20senior%20official%20from%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20detected%20in%20an%20RT-PCR%20positive%20sample%20from%20Karakulam%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram%20district%20of%20the%20southern%20state%20on%20December%208%2C%20Dr%20Rajiv%20Bahl%2C%20Director%20General%20of%20the%20ICMR%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sample%20had%20tested%20RT-PCR%20positive%20on%20November%2018%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2079-year-old%20woman%20had%20mild%20symptoms%20of%20Influenza%20Like%20Illness%20(ILI)%20and%20has%20since%20recovered%20from%20Covid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20an%20increasing%20trend%20of%20COVID-19%20cases%20from%20the%20state%20of%20Kerala%20since%20the%20last%20few%20weeks.%20This%20has%20been%20attributed%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20samples%20from%20ILI%20cases%20being%20referred%20for%20testing%2C%26quot%3B%20Bahl%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20majority%20of%20these%20cases%20are%20clinically%20mild%20and%20the%20patients%20are%20recovering%20on%20their%20own%20at%20their%20homes%2C%20without%20any%20treatment%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20a%20regular%20exercise%20of%20the%20Union%20health%20ministry%2C%20a%20mock%20drill%20at%20all%20health%20facilities%20in%20the%20states%20is%20underway%20to%20assess%20their%20public%20health%20and%20hospital-preparedness%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20activity%2C%20which%20started%20on%20December%2013%2C%20is%20being%20carried%20out%20under%20the%20overall%20supervision%20of%20the%20district%20collectors%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20December%2018%2C%20Bahl%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20ministry%20is%20in%20regular%20touch%20with%20the%20Kerala%20health%20department%20and%20monitoring%20various%20entry%20points%20to%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INSACOG%20is%20a%20network%20of%20genomic%20laboratories%20that%20has%20been%20monitoring%20COVID-19%20in%20India%20from%20a%20genomic%20perspective.%20The%20ICMR%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20consortium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20revised%20surveillance%20guidelines%20in%20the%20context%20of%20COVID-19%2C%20patients%20of%20ILI%20and%20SARI%20are%20tested%20for%20the%20viral%20disease%20and%20the%20positive%20cases%20are%20referred%20for%20whole%20genome%20sequencing%20(WGS).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702736760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fr935u0bo_covid-generic-1200-_625x300_08_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcovid-sub-variant-jn-1-case-detected-in-79-year-old-kerala-woman-4684159%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20case%20of%20COVID-19%20sub-variant%20JN.1%20was%20detected%20in%20Kerala%20on%20December%208%2C%20official%20sources%20said%20on%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcovid-sub-variant-jn-1-case-detected-in-79-year-old-kerala-woman-4684159%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcovid-sub-variant-jn-1-case-detected-in-79-year-old-kerala-woman-4684159%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcovid-sub-variant-jn-1-case-detected-in-79-year-old-kerala-woman-4684159%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Nick'%2C%20a%20Money%20Courier%20and%20a%20Hitman%3A%20What%20New%20Documents%20Say%20About%20The%20Pannun%20Murder%20Plot%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F16222457%2FScreenshot-2023-12-16-at-10.23.5.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20arrived%20at%20V%C3%A1clav%20Havel%20Airport%20in%20Prague%20on%20a%20Friday%20in%20June%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20that%20he%20did%20not%20know%20that%20it%20would%20kickstart%20the%20process%20of%20removing%20the%20secretive%20shroud%20on%20an%20investigation%20that%20would%20encompass%20three%20countries%20and%20be%20pivotal%20in%20the%20United%20States%E2%80%99%20most%20explosive%20charges%20yet%20against%20the%20Indian%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20would%20only%20be%20around%20five%20months%20later%20that%20US%20federal%20prosecutors%20would%20release%20a%20detailed%2015-page%20indictment%20that%20named%20an%20Indian%20national%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20as%20the%20prime%20accused%20for%20hiring%20a%20%E2%80%98hitman%E2%80%99.%20Even%20more%20startling%2C%20the%20indictment%20implicated%20an%20Indian%20government%20official%20in%20masterminding%20the%20unsuccessful%20plot%20to%20assassinate%20a%20Sikh%20separatist%2C%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cnin%20New%20York.%20Pannun%20is%20a%20US%20citizen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20habeas%20corpus%20petition%20submitted%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20this%20week%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20family%20is%20urging%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20active%20involvement%20in%20securing%20his%20return.%20The%20petition%2C%20intriguingly%20titled%20%E2%80%98Mr%20X%20v%2Fs%20the%20Union%20of%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20levels%20serious%20allegations%20against%20the%20US%20and%20Czech%20authorities%20regarding%20his%20treatment%20in%20detention%20but%20also%20reveals%20additional%20details%20about%20the%20investigation%20by%20US%20agencies%20that%20have%20so%20far%20not%20been%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20sought%20a%20response%20from%20the%20Czech%20judicial%20authorities%20about%20the%20new%20allegations%2C%20but%20has%20received%20no%20response%20yet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20writ%20petition%20has%20attached%20the%20US%20Southern%20District%20of%20New%20York%20grand%20jury%E2%80%99s%20sealed%20June%2013%20indictment%20of%20Nikhil%20Gupta.%20It%20also%20includes%20the%20extradition%20request%20presented%20by%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20in%20August%20to%20the%20Czech%20government%2C%20which%20contains%20supporting%20affidavits%20from%20the%20Assistant%20US%20Attorney%20at%20Southern%20District%20of%20New%20York%2C%20Ashley%20C.%20Nicolas%20and%20Drug%20Enforcement%20Agency%20(DEA)%20special%20agent%20Mark%20J.%20Franks.%20These%20provide%20further%20insights%20into%20the%20case%20against%20Gupta%20by%20US%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%2C%20as%20outlined%20in%20the%2015-page%20indictment%20made%20public%20last%20month.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20since%20the%20writ%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20does%20not%20disclose%20the%20name%20of%20the%20petitioner%2C%20but%20only%20refers%20to%20%E2%80%9CMr%20X%E2%80%9D%2C%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20name%20is%20also%20redacted%20in%20the%20annexures%20%E2%80%93%20except%20in%20two%20paragraphs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilar%20to%20the%20sealed%20charges%20filed%20on%20June%2013%2C%20neither%20the%20formal%20extradition%20request%20nor%20the%20affidavits%20make%20any%20reference%20to%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%20agent.%20This%20information%20was%20only%20revealed%20in%20the%20most%20recent%20indictment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnikhil-gupta-pannun-plot-challenges-extradition-order-czech-court%5C%22%3EExclusive%3A%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20Fights%20Extradition%20to%20US%20in%20Czech%20Court%2C%20Fate%20of%20Pannun%20Murder%20Plot%20Will%20Turn%20on%20Outcome%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Four%20jobs%3B%20innocent%20bystanders%3B%20CC-1%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20all%20these%20documents%20highlight%20a%20crucial%20event%20where%20an%20undercover%20agent%2C%20assuming%20the%20role%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98hitman%2C%E2%80%99%20allegedly%20received%20a%20%2415%2C000%20advance%20payment%20through%20a%20middleman.%20Gupta%2C%20introduced%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98hitman%E2%80%99%20by%20an%20alleged%20criminal%20associate%2C%20remained%20unaware%20that%20this%20associate%20was%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20a%20DEA%20informant.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20affidavits%20submitted%20in%20August%2C%20a%20US%20federal%20grand%20jury%20issued%20a%20sealed%20indictment%20of%20Gupta%20just%20four%20days%20later%20after%20the%20money%20handover.%20On%20the%20same%20day%2C%20June%2013%2C%20the%20Southern%20District%20of%20New%20York%20court%20clerk%20issued%20an%20arrest%20warrant%20in%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20name.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20June%2018%2C%20a%20Canadian%20national%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20was%20shot%20and%20killed%20by%20masked%20gunmen.%20In%20the%20evening%2C%20CC-1%20%E2%80%93%20an%20intelligence%20or%20security%20agency%20who%20remains%20unnamed%20%E2%80%93%20had%20shared%20a%20video%20of%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20body%20slumped%20in%20his%20vehicle%20with%20Gupta%2C%20which%20he%20forwarded%20to%20his%20criminal%20friend.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20day%20later%2C%20Gupta%2C%20as%20per%20the%20November%20indictment%2C%20told%20his%20friend%20that%20Nijjar%20had%20also%20been%20one%20of%20the%20targets.%20He%20also%20urged%20him%20to%20expedite%20the%20plan%20to%20assassinate%20the%20Sikh%20American%20lawyer%2C%20but%20to%20be%20cautious%20in%20light%20of%20the%20Canadian%20shooting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20same%20day%2C%20June%2019%2C%20the%20Czech%20Justice%20Ministry%20issued%20a%20provisional%20arrest%20warrant%20in%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20name.%20On%20that%20day%2C%20according%20to%20DEA%20Special%20Agent%20Mark%20Franks%2C%20Gupta%20allegedly%20told%20the%20DEA%20informant%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20plot%2C%20even%20if%20there%20were%20innocent%20bystanders%20around%20the%20%E2%80%98intended%20victim%E2%80%99.%20He%20also%20reportedly%20stressed%20on%20June%2019%20that%20the%20murder%20of%20Sikh%20American%20lawyer%20should%20be%20finished%20within%2011%20days%20and%20promised%20that%20it%20would%20be%20the%20first%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfour%20job%5Bs%5D%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20per%20the%20affidavit.%20The%20fact%20that%20Gupta%20became%20a%20person%20of%20interest%20for%20the%20Czechs%20on%20June%2019%20means%20that%20the%20US%20knew%20of%20his%20future%20travel%20plans%20by%20then.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Forced%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAssistant%20US%20Attorney%20Nicolas%E2%80%99s%20affidavit%20claimed%20that%20Czech%20authorities%20arrested%20Gupta%20on%20June%2030%20and%20seized%20three%20electronic%20devices%20and%20his%20luggage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20writ%20petition%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20a%20different%20version%2C%20with%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20lawyers%20alleging%20that%20US%20officials%20had%20physically%20accessed%20his%20phone%20during%20the%20time%20when%20he%20was%20bundled%20into%20a%20black%20SUV%20from%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20individuals%20took%20the%20petitioner%E2%80%99s%20mobile%20phones%20forcefully%20from%20the%20petitioner%20and%20attached%20a%20device%20to%20it%20as%20they%20continued%20to%20question%20the%20petitioner%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20writ%20petition.%20They%20also%20apparently%20got%20him%20to%20unlock%20his%20iPhone%20with%20the%20Face%20ID%20feature.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20interrogation%2C%20Gupta%20said%20that%20he%20was%20being%20mistaken%20for%20someone%20else%2C%20even%20as%20they%20%E2%80%9Ccontinued%20to%20threaten%20the%20petitioner%20and%20asking%20him%20to%20confess%20to%20allegations%20that%20the%20petitioner%20had%20himself%20heard%20for%20the%20first%20time%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20three%20hours%20with%20American%20agents%20in%20the%20SUV%20which%20circled%20the%20city%2C%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20petition%20claims%20he%20was%20then%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20local%20Czech%20authorities%20and%20detained%20at%20Pankr%C3%A1c%20Prison%20in%20Prague.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20same%20night%2C%20a%20defence%20lawyer%20appointed%20by%20the%20Czech%20authorities%20called%20up%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20son%20to%20inform%20him%20about%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20arrest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20timeline%20provided%20in%20the%20writ%20petition%2C%20he%20was%20presented%20before%20a%20Prague%20court%20on%20July%201%20and%20informed%20of%20the%20charges%20of%20%E2%80%98conspiracy%20to%20murder%E2%80%99%20listed%20in%20the%20June%2013%20sealed%20indictment%20by%20the%20grand%20jury.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGupta%20described%20himself%20as%20a%2052-year-old%20%E2%80%9Cmiddle-class%20businessman%E2%80%9D%20who%20runs%20a%20consultancy%20dealing%20with%20excavation%20and%20import-export%20out%20of%20Delhi.%20His%20family%20consists%20of%20his%20wife%2C%20two%20grown-up%20children%20and%20mother.%20The%20purpose%20of%20his%20travel%20to%20Prague%20via%20Turkey%20was%20for%20%E2%80%9Ctourism%20and%20for%20exploring%20new%20market%20for%20his%20business%20of%20handicraft%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Discussions%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDEA%20special%20agent%20Mark%20Frank%E2%80%99s%20affidavit%20said%20that%20their%20confidential%20informant%20had%20developed%20a%20relationship%20with%20an%20Indian%20calling%20himself%20%E2%80%98Nick%E2%80%99%20from%202016.%20He%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%98Nick%E2%80%99%20was%20identified%20as%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20phone%20records%20and%20reports%20of%20other%20law%20enforcement%20agencies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20next%20seven%20years%2C%20Gupta%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98Confidential%20Informant%E2%80%99%20(referred%20to%20as%20CS%20in%20the%20indictment)%20discussed%20several%20narcotics%20and%20weapon%20trafficking%20deals%2C%20but%20nothing%20came%20to%20fruition%2C%20as%20per%20both%20the%20affidavits%20of%20the%20US%20officials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Nicolas%2C%20while%20the%20Confidential%20Informant%20believed%20that%20Gupta%20was%20a%20drug%20and%20weapons%20trafficker%2C%20the%20latter%20thought%20that%20his%20old%20acquaintance%20was%20a%20Colombian%20cocaine%20supplier.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20DEA%20special%20agent%20claimed%20that%20in%20March%20of%20this%20year%2C%20Gupta%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98Colombian%E2%80%99%20started%20to%20discuss%20a%20new%20firearms%20and%20confidential%20deal.%20Then%20around%20May%2030%2C%20Gupta%20asked%20for%20his%20help%20in%20finding%20someone%20to%20murder%20a%20lawyer%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687016%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20a%20still%20image%20ofthe%20Advance%20Payment%20as%20shown%20in%20the%20DoJ%20indictment%20of%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20and%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECash%20in%20hand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20around%202.30%20pm%2C%20on%20June%209%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98money%20courier%E2%80%99%20handed%20over%20%2415%2C000%20to%20the%20undercover%20agent%2C%20posing%20as%20a%20hitman.%20During%20that%20handover%2C%20Gupta%20called%20up%20the%20%E2%80%98hitman%E2%80%99%20and%20asked%20to%20speak%20with%20the%20money%20courier%2C%20as%20per%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20physical%20handover%20of%20money%20is%20key%20to%20the%20case.%20Special%20Agent%20Marks%20described%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20identification%20as%20being%20linked%20to%20the%20phone%20number%20that%20was%20used%20to%20communicate%20with%20the%20person%20who%20arranged%20the%20%2415%2C000%20payment%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98hitman%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17005913%2Fnick-collage.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17005913%2Fnick-collage.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17005913%2Fnick-collage-300x180.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17005913%2Fnick-collage-1024x614.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689489%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETwo%20photographs%20of%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20attached%20by%20the%20US%20authorities%20in%20their%20extradition%20request%20to%20the%20Czech%20government.%20The%20first%20is%20described%20as%20being%20taken%20by%20U.S.%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20on%20June%2014%2C%202017%2C%20at%20Los%20Angeles%20International%20Airpor%2C%20and%20the%20second%20taken%20by%20U.S.%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20on%20December%2012%2C%202016%2C%20at%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20Airport.%20The%20Wire%20has%20blurred%20the%20images.*%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20identified%20Gupta%20based%20on%20two%20photographs%20taken%20at%20the%20border%20when%20the%20Indian%20travelled%20to%20US%20in%202016%20and%202017.%20%E2%80%9CI%20compared%20both%20photographs%20of%20%E2%80%94%20to%20recordings%20of%20video%20calls%20between%20the%20Con%EF%AC%81dential%20Informant%20and%20the%20Undercover%20Agent%20and%20the%20person%20who%20paid%20to%20have%20the%20Intended%20Victim%20murdered%20via%20the%20Phone%20Number%2C%20and%20determined%20that%20(Redacted)%E2%80%99s%20photographs%20match%20the%20person%20depicted%20in%20the%20video%20calls%20who%20paid%20to%20have%20the%20Intended%20Victim%20murdered%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20DEA%20special%20agent%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Human%20rights%20violations%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20writ%20petition%20filed%20by%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20family%20in%20the%20Indian%20Supreme%20Court%20did%20not%20deal%20with%20the%20specific%20details%20of%20the%20two%20indictments%2C%20as%20Gupta%20gave%20a%20blanket%20dismissal%20stating%20that%20that%20the%20allegations%20were%20made%20against%20a%20%E2%80%98Nick%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20alias%20which%20he%20has%20never%20used.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20submission%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20a%20long%20list%20of%20alleged%20violations%20of%20human%20rights%20that%20Gupta%20suffered%20in%20the%20last%20five%20months%20in%20Czech%20prisons%20in%20Prague%20and%20Brno.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20first%20fortnight%2C%20he%20claimed%20to%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20eat%20non-vegetarian%20food%20in%20the%20prison%2C%20despite%20informing%20them%20of%20his%20religious%20dietary%20practices.%20He%20also%20claims%20that%20his%20defence%20counsel%20appointed%20by%20Czech%20authorities%20was%20telling%20him%20to%20waive%20off%20his%20right%20to%20fight%20the%20extradition%2C%20which%20was%20not%20in%20his%20client%E2%80%99s%20best%20interests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20claimed%20that%20Czech%20authorities%20used%20the%20excuse%20that%20he%20had%20contracted%20a%20communicable%20blood%20infection%20to%20put%20him%20in%20solitary%20confinement%2C%20as%20well%20as%20shift%20him%20to%20a%20distant%20prison%2C%20to%20stop%20his%20meeting%20with%20any%20Indian%20embassy%20official.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20only%20meeting%20that%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20had%20with%20an%20embassy%20official%20was%20on%20July%2020.%20He%20also%20claimed%20that%20phone%20calls%20to%20his%20family%20in%20India%20were%20restricted%2C%20as%20part%20of%20pressure%20tactics%20used%20against%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%20to%20facing%20questioning%20upon%20exiting%20Prague%20airport%20on%20June%2030%2C%20Gupta%20asserted%20that%20he%20underwent%20a%20formal%20interview%20with%20agents%20from%20the%20DEA%2C%20CIA%2C%20and%20a%20SDNY%20prosecutor%20on%20October%205%2C%20an%20event%20purportedly%20recorded%20on%20video.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnikhil-gupta-pannun-plot-challenges-extradition-order-czech-court%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20asked%20the%20Czech%20Justice%20Ministry%20last%20week%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20whether%20the%20US%20had%20requested%20or%20been%20granted%20access%20to%20Gupta.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20case%2C%20there%20is%20%5Ba%5D%20pre-trial%20proceeding%20being%20conducted%20in%20a%20foreign%20state%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Public%20Prosecutor%E2%80%99s%20Office%20is%20competent%20to%20accept%20a%20request%20of%20the%20foreign%20authority%20for%20legal%20assistance%3B%20otherwise%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Justice%20is%20competent.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Justice%20has%20not%20received%20any%20formal%20requests%20for%20legal%20assistance%20concerning%20the%20interrogation%20of%20Mr%20Gupta%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20replied.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-pannun-modi-foreign-policy-national-interest%5C%22%3EFrom%20Nijjar%20to%20Pannun%2C%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Recklessness%20is%20Undermining%20National%20Interest%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInconsistency%20in%20passport%20number%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20inconsistency%20arises%20between%20the%20US%20documents%20and%20the%20applications%20filed%20by%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20family%20concerning%20his%20passport%20number.%20The%20US%20agents%20have%20listed%20a%20passport%20for%20Gupta%20that%20was%20apparently%20issued%20in%20March%20this%20year.%20But%2C%20that%20is%20different%20from%20the%20number%20provided%20by%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20son%20and%20daughter%20in%20their%20communication%20requesting%20help%20to%20the%20MEA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%2010%2C%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20son%20wrote%20a%20long-detailed%20email%20to%20Indian%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20that%20listed%20out%20the%20treatment%20of%20their%20father%20in%20Czech%20Republic.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20month%20later%2C%20the%20Municipal%20Court%20in%20Prague%20ruled%20that%20the%20extradition%20request%20was%20admissible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20writ%20petition%20on%20behalf%20of%20Gupta%20claimed%20that%20that%20an%20appeal%20was%20not%20filed%20before%20the%20Higher%20Court%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctyped%20copy%20of%20the%20order%20has%20not%20been%20made%20available%20to%20the%20Petitioner%20or%20his%20Attorney%20at%20Prague%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Czech%20Justice%20ministry%20had%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20last%20week%20that%20there%20was%20a%20delay%20in%20enforcing%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20on%20extradition%20as%20the%20petitioner%2C%20that%20is%20Gupta%2C%20had%20filed%20a%20complaint.%20%E2%80%9CMr%20Gupta%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20(i.e.%20an%20ordinary%20remedy)%20against%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20municipal%20court%20in%20Prague%20on%20the%20admissibility%20of%20extradition%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Justice%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Vladimir%20%C5%98epka.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20mentioned%20above%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20official%20clarification%20from%20Prague%20on%20the%20new%20allegations%20made%20by%20Gupta%20and%20his%20family%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E*Note%3A%20Though%20the%20photograph%20of%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20forms%20part%20of%20the%20petition%20filed%20by%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20and%20his%20family%20in%20the%20case%20and%20is%20now%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20The%20Wire%20has%20decided%20to%20blur%20his%20features%20as%20they%20have%20expressed%20fears%20about%20his%20security%20in%20the%20same%20petition.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702736435000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F16194448%2FScreenshot-2023-12-16-at-7.44.10.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnikhil-gupta-pannun-assassination-plot-documents%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20extradition%20request%20to%20the%20Czech%20government%20includes%20the%20original%20sealed%20indictment%20against%20'Nick'%20and%20accompanying%20affidavits%20which%20highlight%20a%20crucial%20event%20where%20an%20undercover%20agent%2C%20assuming%20the%20role%20of%20a%20'hitman%2C'%20received%20a%20%2415%2C000%20advance%20payment%20through%20a%20middleman.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnikhil-gupta-pannun-assassination-plot-documents%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Almost%20300%20people%20make%20Channel%20boat%20crossings%20in%20one%20day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702736280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskynews-migration-channel-crossing_6372188.jpg%3F20231125173709%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Falmost-300-people-make-english-channel-boat-crossings-in-single-day-13031712%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Almost%20300%20people%20crossed%20the%20English%20Channel%20on%20the%20same%20day%20one%20person%20died.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A381%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Falmost-300-people-make-english-channel-boat-crossings-in-single-day-13031712%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Falmost-300-people-make-english-ch