dy%20with%20the%20UP%20police%20in%20the%20Umesh%20Pal%20murder%20case.%20Umesh%20Pal%20was%20a%20key%20witness%20in%20the%20murder%20case%20of%20BSP%20MLA%20Raju%20Pal%2C%20in%20which%20the%20ex-MP%20was%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Larger%20conspiracy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArguing%20for%20Ansari%2C%20senior%20counsel%20Kapil%20Sibal%20submitted%20that%20despite%20directions%20by%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20Ansari%2C%20Sanjeev%20Maheshwari%20alias%20Jeeva%20%E2%80%93%20a%20co-accused%20of%20Ansari%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20BJP%20MLA%20Krishnanand%20Rai%20in%202005%20%E2%80%93%20was%20shot%20dead%20inside%20a%20courtroom%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20June%208%2C%202023%2C%20while%20he%20was%20being%20produced%20from%20jail%20custody%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20had%20in%20May%202023%2C%20on%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20Ansari%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20directed%20the%20DGP%20UP%20to%20ensure%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20security%20inside%20the%20jail%20as%20well%20as%20outside%20it.%20The%20court%20had%20directed%20the%20police%20to%20ensure%20that%20%E2%80%9Cfull%20security%E2%80%9D%20be%20given%20to%20Ansari%20while%20shifting%20him%20from%20one%20jail%20to%20another%20and%20while%20producing%20him%20before%20any%20court%20from%20jail%20and%20on%20the%20way.%20The%20HC%20had%20taken%20into%20consideration%20the%20murder%20of%20Atiq%20Ahmad%20and%20his%20brother%20while%20passing%20the%20directions%2C%20and%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMedia%20person%20would%20not%20be%20permitted%20to%20interview%20him.%20He%20would%20be%20accompanied%20by%20the%20police%20personnel%20during%20his%20ingress%20and%20egress%20from%20jail.%20This%20order%20is%20being%20passed%20seeing%20the%20recent%20episode%20which%20occurred%20in%20the%20State%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20wherein%20in%20the%20garb%20of%20media%20persons%20some%20criminals%20had%20killed%20two%20under%20trial%20prisoners%2C%20who%20were%20in%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20Police%20Personnel%2C%20which%20matters%20are%20pending%20before%20the%20Apex%20Court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Mukhtar%E2%80%99s%20son%20Umar%20accused%20the%20Adityanath%20government%20of%20taking%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinimical%20position%E2%80%9D%20against%20the%20former%20MLA%20and%20hatching%20a%20%E2%80%9Clarger%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20to%20eliminate%20him%20while%20he%20is%20in%20jail.%20The%20threat%20perception%20was%20based%20on%20%E2%80%9Creliable%20information%E2%80%9D%20Mukhtar%20had%20received%20that%20his%20life%20was%20in%20grave%20danger%20and%20that%20there%20%E2%80%9Cis%20a%20conspiracy%20afoot%20involving%20several%20actors%20within%20the%20state%20establishment%E2%80%9D%20to%20assassinate%20him%20in%20Banda%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Gangster%20Mukhtar%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-time%20former%20MLA%20from%20Mau%20in%20eastern%20UP%2C%20Mukhtar%20has%20for%20long%20been%20under%20the%20radar%20of%20the%20Adityanath%20government%2C%20which%20after%20coming%20to%20power%20in%202017%20unleashed%20the%20police%20and%20the%20force%20of%20the%20administration%20against%20him%2C%20his%20family%20and%20supporters.%20The%20state%20government%20designated%20Mukhtar%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgangster%E2%80%9D%20and%20head%20of%20gang%20IS191%2C%20and%20lodged%20numerous%20criminal%20cases%20against%20him%2C%20his%20sons%2C%20including%20current%20MLA%20Abbas%20Ansari%2C%20his%20brother%20and%20former%20MP%20Afzal%20Ansari%20and%20other%20associates.%20The%20government%20has%20seized%2C%20demolished%20and%20freed%20from%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20occupation%E2%80%9D%20property%20worth%20Rs%20605%20crores%20belonging%20to%20the%20Ansari%20family%2C%20said%20police.%20Out%20of%20this%2C%20about%20Rs%20318%20crores%20worth%20of%20property%20was%20seized%20by%20the%20government%20under%20Section%2014%20(1)%20of%20the%20contentious%20Gangsters%20Act%2C%20which%20empowers%20the%20district%20magistrate%20to%20attach%20properties%20of%20people%20after%20designating%20them%20as%20gangsters.%20Under%20the%20Adityanath%20rule%2C%20this%20law%20has%20been%20used%20without%20restraint%20against%20suspected%20criminals%20as%20well%20as%20opposition%20leaders%20and%20ordinary%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fwhy-are-criminals-called-gunda-mafia-or-don%5C%22%3EWhy%20Are%20Criminals%20Called%20%E2%80%98Goonda%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Mafia%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20it%20had%20also%20demolished%2C%20seized%20or%20freed%20property%20from%20the%20Ansaris%20under%20other%20laws%20worth%20Rs%20287%20crores.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20police%20said%20it%20had%20shut%20down%20businesses%20%E2%80%93%20tender%2C%20contract%20and%20firms%20%E2%80%93%20linked%20to%20Ansari%20amounting%20to%20Rs%20215%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20shot%20dead%20five%20persons%20linked%20to%20Ansari%20in%20alleged%20encounters%20and%20taken%20legal%20action%20against%20292%20persons%20linked%20to%20him%3B%20booked%20164%20of%20his%20associates%20under%20the%20Gangsters%20Act%2C%20six%20under%20the%20National%20Security%20Act%2C%2067%20under%20the%20Gangsters%20Act%2C%20expelled%2060%20of%20his%20associates%20from%20their%20districts%2C%20arrested%20186%20and%20cancelled%20175%20weapon%20licences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVarious%20cases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%2015%20months%2C%20he%20has%20been%20convicted%20in%20seven%20different%20cases.%20The%20seventh%20conviction%20came%20on%20December%2015%2C%20when%20a%20court%20in%20Varanasi%20sentenced%20him%20to%20six%20years%20and%20five%20months%20in%20prison%20for%20a%20case%20lodged%20against%20him%20in%201997%20on%20charges%20of%20criminal%20intimidation.%20The%20other%20convictions%20include%20a%20life%20sentence%20awarded%20to%20him%20by%20a%20Varanasi%20court%20in%20June%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20Awadesh%20Rai%2C%20the%20brother%20of%20Congress%20state%20president%20Ajay%20Rai%2C%20and%20the%2010%20years%20imprisonment%20awarded%20to%20him%20for%20kidnapping%20a%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20leader%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20murder%20of%20Krishnanand%20Rai%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnsari%20has%2065%20cases%20lodged%20against%20him%2C%20said%20UP%20police%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20trying%20to%20get%20him%20convicted%20in%20the%2021%20cases%20he%20was%20facing%20trial%20in%20through%20%E2%80%9Cexcellent%20coordination%E2%80%9D%20and%20constant%20monitoring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Umar%20Ansari%20said%20that%20out%20of%20the%20persons%20accused%20of%20murdering%20Rai%2C%20four%2C%20including%20Jeeva%20(mentioned%20above)%20had%20already%20been%20murdered.%20While%20Firdaus%20was%20gunned%20down%20by%20the%20STF%20in%202006%2C%20Prem%20Prakash%20Singh%20alias%20Munna%20Bajrangi%20was%20murdered%20in%20Baghpat%20jail%20in%202018%20by%20another%20convicted%20gangster%20Sunil%20Rathi.%20More%20than%20a%20week%20before%20his%20murder%20Bajrangi%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Seema%20Singh%20had%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20June%2029%20that%20year%20alleged%20that%20the%20UP%20police%20along%20with%20some%20political%20leaders%20and%20officials%20were%20conspiring%20to%20get%20him%20eliminated%20outside%20the%20jail%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfake%20encounter.%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20had%20also%20claimed%20that%20during%20his%20stay%20in%20Jhansi%20jail%20there%20had%20been%20an%20attempt%20to%20poison%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20aide%20of%20Mukhtar%2C%20Rakesh%20Pandey%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20the%20police%20in%20an%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cencounter%E2%80%9D%20in%20August%202020%20after%20the%20SUV%20he%20was%20purportedly%20travelling%20in%20along%20with%20four%20other%20persons%20cra