administration%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20on%20the%20inquiry%20being%20conducted%20into%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20raised%20by%20the%20woman%20judge.%20The%20CJI%20is%20yet%20to%20publicly%20respond%20to%20the%20matter%20or%20issue%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20system%20of%20redressal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20sexually%20harassed%20by%20one%20particular%20district%20judge%20and%20his%20associates.%20I%20was%20told%20to%20meet%20the%20district%20judge%20at%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20civil%20judge%20wrote%20in%20her%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAlthough%20she%20does%20not%20state%20specific%20instances%20or%20names%20the%20accused%2C%20her%20letter%20provides%20a%20clear%20glimpse%20of%20the%20distressing%20experience%20she%20had%20to%20go%20through%20in%20order%20to%20seek%20justice%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShe%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20abused%20verbally%20in%20open%20court%20with%20a%20misogynist%20slur%20and%20that%20she%20had%20even%20tried%20to%20kill%20herself%20through%20suicide.%20The%20judge%20reportedly%20endured%20the%20harassment%20and%20abuse%20during%20her%20earlier%20posting%20in%20another%20district%20close%20to%20the%20capital%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20sexually%20harassed%20to%20the%20very%20limit.%20I%20have%20been%20treated%20like%20utter%20garbage.%20I%20feel%20like%20an%20unwanted%20insect.%20And%20I%20hoped%20to%20provide%20justice%20to%20others.%20What%20naive%20me!%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20woman%20judge%2C%20whose%20identity%20and%20location%20are%20not%20being%20disclosed%20to%20protect%20her%20privacy%20as%20mandated%20by%20law%2C%20said%20she%20had%C2%A0%20complained%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20and%20the%20administrative%20judge%20in%202022%20but%20that%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20till%20date.%20Nobody%20had%20even%20bothered%20to%20ask%20why%20she%20was%20distressed%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20July%2C%202023%20she%20complained%20to%20the%20Internal%20Complaints%20Committee%20(ICC)%20of%20the%20high%20court%20but%20it%20%E2%80%9Ctook%20six%20months%20and%20a%20thousand%20emails%E2%80%9D%20just%20to%20start%20an%20enquiry%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20proposed%20enquiry%20is%20also%20a%20farce%20and%20a%20sham.%20The%20witnesses%20in%20the%20enquiry%20are%20immediate%20subordinates%20of%20the%20district%20judge%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20arguing%20that%20for%20a%20fair%20enquiry%20the%20witnesses%20ought%20not%20to%20be%20in%20the%20administrative%20control%20of%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20the%20committee%20expects%20the%20witnesses%20to%20depose%20against%20their%20boss%20is%20beyond%20my%20understanding.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20civil%20judge%20said%20she%20had%20requested%20that%20the%20accused%20district%20judge%20be%20transferred%20during%20the%20pendency%20of%20the%20enquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fgender-bias-women-workplace-sexual-harassment-posh-kerala-hc%5C%22%3E%20Gender%20Bias%20Against%20Women%20at%20Workplace%20Is%20Not%20Sexual%20Harassment%20Under%20POSH%3A%20Kerala%20HC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPetition%20dismissed%20at%20SC%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShe%20then%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20with%20her%20prayer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Hrishikesh%20Roy%20and%20Sandeep%20Mehta%20on%20December%2013%20dismissed%20a%20writ%20petition%20filed