0Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20appear%20to%20have%20used%20the%20massive%20cash%20recovery%20in%20the%20raids%20%E2%80%93%20said%20to%20be%20the%20biggest-ever%20in%20a%20single%20operation%20by%20the%20income%20tax%20department%20%E2%80%93%20to%20paint%20a%20black%20picture%20of%20the%20grand%20old%20party%2C%20which%20is%20still%20reeling%20under%20the%20impact%20of%20poll%20drubbings%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20top-level%20BJP%20leaders%20to%20react%20to%20the%20seizure%20of%20an%20unprecedented%20amount%20of%20cash%20from%20the%20premises%20linked%20to%20the%20family%20members%20of%20Sahu%2C%20a%20big%20name%20in%20Jharkhand%20politics.%20Taking%20to%20X%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20countrymen%20should%20look%20at%20the%20pile%20of%20these%20notes%20and%20then%20listen%20to%20the%20honest%20%E2%80%98speeches%E2%80%99%20of%20their%20leaders%E2%80%A6%20Whatever%20has%20been%20looted%20from%20the%20public%2C%20every%20penny%20will%20have%20to%20be%20returned%2C%20this%20is%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20guarantee.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%9F%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%A2%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%96%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%94%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%AB%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%93%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%88%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E2%80%98%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A3%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%82%E2%80%99%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%E2%80%A6%20%F0%9F%98%82%F0%9F%98%82%F0%9F%98%82%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn