om%20top%20BJP%20leaders%20on%20the%20seizure%2C%20the%20MP%20from%20Jharkhand%20has%20not%20been%20arrested.%20He%20only%20reacted%20to%20the%20issue%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcong-mp-dhiraj-sahu-10-day-i-t-raids-end-highest-ever-cash-haul-9070112%2F%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20news%20agency%20ANI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20happening%20today%20makes%20me%20sad.%20I%20can%20admit%20that%20the%20money%20that%20has%20been%20recovered%20belongs%20to%20my%20firm%E2%80%A6%20The%20cash%20that%20has%20been%20recovered%20is%20related%20to%20my%20liquor%20firms%2C%20it%20is%20the%20proceedings%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20liquor%E2%80%A6%20This%20money%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20Congress%20or%20any%20other%20political%20party%20as%20is%20being%20said%E2%80%A6%20The%20money%20is%20not%20all%20mine%2C%20it%20belongs%20to%20my%20family%20and%20other%20related%20firms%E2%80%A6I-T%20has%20raided%20now%2C%20I%20will%20give%20account%20for%20everything.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell-known%20political%20analyst%20professor%20Rajar%20Kujur%20finds%20this%20bizarre.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20was%20Sahu%20not%20arrested%3F%20He%20is%20no%20small%20person%20and%20if%20he%20is%20being%20linked%20to%20the%20seized%20cash%20in%20any%20way%2C%20he%20should%20by%20now%20have%20been%20in%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20agency%20and%20his%20statement%20should%20have%20been%20taken.%20That%20may%20put%20an%20end%20to%20this%20entire%20controversy%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kujur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20laws%20regarding%20economic%20offences%20as%20weak%20and%20liable%20to%20be%20exploited%20by%20influential%20people%20Kujor%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHad%20the%20laws%20been%20strong%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20irregularities%20that%20the%20IT%20suspects%20the%20Sahu%20family%20to%20have%20carried%20out%20would%20not%20have%20taken%20place.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20reactions%20of%20political%20parties%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThough%20the%20seizure%20of%20cash%20is%20a%20reality%2C%20the%20politics%20over%20it%20is%20distasteful%20and%20allegations%20and%20counter-allegations%20are%20being%20made%20by%20the%20parties%20only%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20next%20elections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20tremors%20in%20Odisha%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20tremors%20of%20the%20raids%20that%20began%20on%20December%206%20and%20lasted%20over%20four%20days%20are%20still%20being%20felt%20in%20Odisha%20from%20where%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20around%20Rs%20350%20crore%20was%20recovered.%20Though%20seizures%20were%20also%20made%20from%20locations%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20West%20Bengal%2C%20major%20recoveries%20were%20made%20from%20Bolangir%2C%20Sambalpur%2C%20Sundergarh%20and%20Bhubaneswar%20in%20Odisha%2C%20the%20main%20hub%20of%20the%20Sahu%20family%E2%80%99s%20liquor%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20has%20also%20triggered%20a%20blame%20game%20among%20the%20major%20political%20parties%20in%20Odisha%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20targeting%20both%20Congress%20and%20the%20Naveen%20Patnaik-led%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD).%20Senior%20saffron%20party%20leaders%20appear%20convinced%20that%20the%20cash%20was%20stashed%20at%20the%20business%20establishments%20of%20the%20Sahu%20family%20with%20the%20knowledge%20of%20BJD%20leadership%20and%20would%20have%20been%20at%20the%20disposal%20of%20the%20regional%20party%20at%20the%20time%20of%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20bulk%20of%20the%20seized%20cash%20was%20recovered%20from%20Bolangir%2C%20which%20is%20known%20to%20be%20a%20poor%20and%20backward%20district.%20The%20money%20was%20obviously%20stashed%20there%20to%20avoid%20suspicion.%20Nobody%20would%20imagine%20such%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20cash%20being%20hidden%20somewhere%20in%20Bolangir.%20The%20ruling%20BJD%2C%20which%20was%20preparing%20for%20early%20elections%2C%20perhaps%20in%20December%2C%20knew%20about%20it%20and%20would%20have%20used%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20alleged%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Loisingha%20MLA%20Mukesh%20Mahaling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahaling%2C%20whose%20constituency%20is%20part%20of%20Bolangir%20district%2C%20alleged%20that%20unscrupulous%20elements%20have%20entered%20the%20liquor%20trade%20in%20the%20state%20with%20the%20government%20turning%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20the%20irregularities.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Odisha%20government%E2%80%99s%20liquor%20policy%20is%20faulty%20with%20no%20control%20of%20traders.%20Licences%20are%20renewed%20at%20will%20and%20they%20promote%20whoever%20they%20want%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20MLA%2C%20who%20is%20convinced%20that%20liquor%20barons%20and%20the%20BJD%20leadership%20are%20working%20hand%20in%20glove.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20since%20the%20BJD%20government%20presented%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fodisha-finance-minister-presents-supplementary-budget-of-28200-crore%2Farticle67335018.ece%23%3A%5C%22%3Esupplementary%20budget%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20September%2C%20during%20the%20monsoon%20session%20of%20the%20state%20assembly%20instead%20of%20the%20usual%20practice%20of%20doing%20so%20in%20the%20winter%20session%2C%20it%20indicated%20that%20the%20party%20wants%20to%20hold%20early%20elections.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20money%20stashed%20away%20by%20%5BSahu%E2%80%99s%20family%5D%20and%20recovered%20by%20the%20IT%20department%20would%20have%20been%20used%20by%20the%20BJD%20in%20the%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20BJD%20MLA%20and%20former%20minister%20Amar%20Satpathy%20rubbished%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20and%20demanded%20a%20thorough%20probe%20into%20the%20issue%2C%20Congress%20veteran%20Ganeshwar%20Behera%20demanded%20a%20completely%20impartial%20inquiry%20to%20bring%20out%20the%20truth.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20law%20should%20take%20its%20course%20in%20the%20matter%20and%20anyone%20found%20guilty%20of%20corruption%20should%20be%20punished.%20But%20for%20the%20whole%20truth%20to%20come%20out%2C%20we%20need%20an%20independent%20inquiry.%20We%20want%20a%20probe%20by%20a%20court-monitored%20SIT.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20trust%20IT%2C%20ED%20or%20CBI%20as%20they%20are%20all%20biased%20and%20act%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20central%20BJP%20leaders%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Behera.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20vast%20empire%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20IT%20officials%20are%20said%20to%20be%20probing%20deeper%20into%20the%20business%20interests%20of%20the%20Sahu%20family%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20the%20liquor%20business%20for%20several%20decades.%20The%20family%20owns%20the%20BDPL%20group%20which%20comprises%20four%20companies%2C%20the%20most%20prominent%20ones%20being%20Boudh%20Distillery%20Private%20Limited%20based%20in%20western%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Boudh%20district%20and%20Baldeo%20Sahu%20Infra%20Private%20Limited%20based%20in%20Bolangir.%20The%20business%20was%20established%20by%20Rai%20Saheb%20Baldeo%20Sahu%2C%20the%20late%20father%20of%20Dhiraj%20Sahu%2C%20and%20today%20has%20country%20liquor%20and%20Indian%20Made%20Foreign%20Liquor%20(IMFL)%20shops%20all%20over%20Jharkhand%2C%20Odisha%20and%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20the%20group%20dominates%20the%20country%20liquor%20manufacturing%20and%20marketing%20business%20in%20Odisha%20with%20control%20over%20250%20country%20liquor%20units%20in%20the%20western%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20where%20%3Cem%3Emahua%3C%2Fem%3E-based%20liquor%20has%20been%20in%20high%20demand%20traditionally.%20The%20Boudh%20Distillery%20Private%20Ltd%2C%20the%20flagship%20company%20of%20the%20group%2C%20has%20a%20near%20monopoly%20not%20only%20in%20Odisha%20but%20also%20in%20Jharkhand.%20It%20also%20supplies%20spirits%20for%20manufacturing%20IMFL%20in%20Odisha%2C%20where%20the%20group%20is%20said%20to%20account%20for%20about%2080%25%20of%20sales%20of%20spirits%20supplied%20to%20bottling%20plants%20in%20Berhampur%2C%20Khurda%2C%20Cuttack%2C%20Sambalpur%20and%20Rayagada.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702712886000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F16130459%2FScreenshot-2023-12-16-at-1.04.05%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fit-raids-cash-seizure-congress-mp-dhiraj-sahur-liquor-business-political-blame-game%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dhiraj%20Sahu%2C%20in%20his%20first%20reaction%20to%20the%20raids%20on%20Friday%2C%20said%20the%20Rs%20350%20crore%20that%20was%20seized%20was%20the%20proceeds%20of%20his%20family%20liquor%20business%20and%20he%20can%20account%20for%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fit-raids-cash-seizure-congress-mp-dhiraj-sahur-liquor-business-political-blame-game%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20issues%20revised%20order%20to%20allow%20use%20of%20sugarcane%20juice%20to%20make%20ethanol%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702710612000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2019-03%2F27%2Ffull%2F1553627795-1514.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fagriculture%2Fgovt-issues-revised-order-to-allow-use-of-sugarcane-juice-to-make-ethanol-123121600218_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20diversion%20of%20sugarcane%20juice%20and%20B%20heavy%20molasses%20is%20allowed%20for%20production%20of%20rectified%20spirit%20and%20extra%20neutral%20alcohol%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20directive%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fagriculture%2Fgovt-issues-revised-order-to-allow-use-of-sugarcane-juice-to-make-ethanol-123121600218_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fagriculture%2Fgovt-issues-revised-order-to-allow-use-of-sugarcane-juice-to-make-ethanol-123121600218_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fagriculture%2Fgovt-issues-revised-order-to-allow-use-of-sugarcane-juice-to-make-ethanol-123121600218_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22USCIRF%20Alarmed%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Increased%20Transnational%20Targeting%E2%80%99%20of%20Religious%20Minorities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F02083207%2FUntitled-design-7.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20United%20States%20Commission%20on%20International%20Religious%20Freedom%20(USCIRF)%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscirf.gov%2Fnews-room%2Freleases-statements%2Fuscirf-deeply-concerned-indias-transnational-repression-against%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eissued%20a%20detailed%20statement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20again%20called%20upon%20the%20Joe%20Biden%20administration%20to%20designate%20India%20a%20Country%20of%20Particular%20Concern%2C%20or%20CPC.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20said%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Calarmed%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20increased%20transnational%20targeting%20of%20religious%20minorities%20and%20those%20advocating%20on%20their%20behalf.%20Recent%20efforts%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20silence%20activists%2C%20journalists%2C%20and%20lawyers%20abroad%20pose%20a%20serious%20threat%20to%20religious%20freedom%E2%80%9D.%20Due%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Csystematic%2C%20ongoing%2C%20and%20egregious%20violations%20of%20freedom%20of%20religion%20or%20belief%E2%80%9D%2C%20USCIRF%20implored%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20State%20to%20designate%20India%20a%20CPC.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUSCIRF%20commissioner%20Stephen%20Schneck%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Sikh%20activist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20Canada%20and%20the%20plot%20to%20kill%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20in%20the%20United%20States%20are%20deeply%20troubling%2C%20and%20represent%20a%20severe%20escalation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20silence%20religious%20minorities%20and%20human%20rights%20defenders%20both%20within%20its%20country%20and%20abroad%E2%80%A6%20We%20call%20on%20the%20Biden%20administration%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20perpetration%20of%20particularly%20severe%20religious%20freedom%20violations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETransnational%20repression%20is%20described%20by%20the%20bipartisan%20commission%20as%20%E2%80%9Cwhen%20states%20use%20intimidation%2C%20harassment%2C%20or%20violence%20against%20those%20living%20outside%20their%20borders.%20Transnational%20repression%20campaigns%20often%20target%20political%20and%20human%20rights%20activists%2C%20journalists%2C%20and%20members%20of%20religious%20and%20ethnic%20minority%20groups.%20In%20extreme%20cases%2C%20tactics%20include%20detention%2C%20reprisals%20against%20family%20members%2C%20kidnapping%2C%20or%2C%20as%20illustrated%20by%20India%2C%20assassinations.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Canadian%20prime%20minister%20and%20US%20federal%20prosecutors%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-pannun-modi-foreign-policy-national-interest%5C%22%3Ealleged%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Indian%20agents%20played%20a%20role%20in%20plotting%20the%20murders%20of%20US%20and%20Canadian%20nationals%20who%20are%20Khalistan%20advocates.%20The%20Indian%20government%20forcefully%20rejected%20Justin%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20but%20has%20set%20up%20an%20inquiry%20to%20look%20into%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20claims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUSCIRF%20is%20an%20autonomous%20and%20cross-party%20federal%20government%20organisation%20that%20scrutinises%2C%20examines%2C%20and%20discloses%20global%20religious%20freedom%20violations.%20Its%20recommendations%20are%20non-obligatory%20for%20the%20US%20state%20department%2C%20which%20has%20ignored%20the%20commission%E2%80%99s%20calls%20to%20designate%20India%20as%20CPC%20for%20the%20past%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20commission%2C%20whose%20hearings%20and%20reports%20have%20flagged%20rising%20cases%20of%20attacks%20and%20intimidation%20of%20religious%20minorities%2C%20civil%20society%20and%20human%20rights%20activists%20in%20India%2C%20went%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20authorities%20have%20used%20spyware%20and%20online%20harassment%20campaigns%20to%20target%20and%20intimidate%20journalists%20and%20activists%20abroad%20advocating%20on%20behalf%20of%20religious%20minorities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20noted%20the%20attacks%20on%20the%20American%20journalist%20who%20questioned%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20in%20Washington%20in%20June%20this%20year.%20%E2%80%9CComments%20from%20the%20head%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20(BJP)%20information%20and%20technology%20department%2C%20Amit%20Malviya%2C%20prompted%20an%20online%20campaign%20against%20U.S.%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20journalist%20Sabrina%20Siddiqui%20for%20posing%20a%20question%20about%20religious%20freedom%20conditions%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWithin%20its%20own%20borders%2C%20Indian%20authorities%20have%20repeatedly%20used%20draconian%20legislation%20like%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%20and%20anti-conversion%20laws%20to%20systematically%20crack%20down%20on%20religious%20minorities%2C%20journalists%2C%20and%20activists%2C%E2%80%9D%20USCIRF%20commissioner%20David%20Curry%20said.%20%E2%80%9CExtending%20this%20repression%20to%20target%20religious%20minorities%20from%20India%20living%20abroad%2C%20including%20intimidation%20tactics%20against%20journalists%2C%20is%20especially%20dangerous%20and%20cannot%20be%20ignored.%20We%20urge%20the%20US%20government%20to%20continue%20its%20active%20engagement%20with%20senior%20Indian%20officials%20and%20international%20partners%20to%20ensure%20religious%20minorities%20can%20live%20and%20express%20themselves%20without%20fear%20of%20reprisal%2C%20whether%20in%20India%20or%20elsewhere%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20USCIRF%20also%20published%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscirf.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2023%2520India%2520Apostasy%2520Issue%2520Update.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eissue%20update%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20state-level%20anti-conversion%20laws%2C%20saying%20they%20target%20religious%20minorities.%20In%20September%202023%2C%20USCIRF%20held%20a%20hearing%20on%20religious%20freedom%20conditions%20in%20India%20and%20how%20the%20US%20government%20can%20work%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20address%20any%20violations.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fuscirf-once-again-raises-concern-over-declining-religious-freedom-in-india%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20October%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20Commission%20called%20on%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20release%2037%20individuals%20across%20multiple%20faiths%20jailed%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpeaceful%20exercise%20of%20their%20freedom%20of%20religion%20or%20belief.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-religious-freedom-watchdog-implores-biden-administration-designate-india-2023-12-16%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EReuters%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20Indian%20embassy%20in%20Washington%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20has%20consistently%20rejected%20the%20USCIRF%E2%80%99s%20reports%2C%20calling%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-lashes-out-uscirf%5C%22%3Ecommission%E2%80%99s%20most%20recent%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmisrepresentation%20of%20facts%E2%80%9D%20and%20making%20%E2%80%9Cbiased%20and%20motivated%20comments%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702708180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F02083207%2FUntitled-design-7.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fuscirf-india-transnational-targeting-religious-minorities-cpc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bipartisan%20commission%20implored%20the%20US%20government%20to%20desginate%20India%20as%20a%20country%20of%20particular%20concern%20for%20religious%20freedom%20due%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bsystematic%2C%20ongoing%2C%20and%20egregious%20violations%20of%20freedom%20of%20religion%20or%20belief%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fuscirf-india-transnational-targeting-religious-minorities-cpc%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20Group%20acquires%20majority%20stake%20in%20news%20agency%20IANS%20for%20undisclosed%20sum%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702706716000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F14%2Ffull%2F1691975779-7461.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fadani-group-acquires-majority-stake-in-news-agency-ians-for-undisclosed-sum-123121600208_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adani%20had%20forayed%20into%20media%20business%20in%20March%20last%20year%20when%20it%20acquired%20Quintillion%20Business%20Media%2C