%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Protests%20Erupt%20in%20Israel%20After%20IDF%20Says%20It%20'Accidentally%20Killed'%20Three%20Hostages%20in%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F16112233%2FIDF_depth_corps_exercises._IV.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20on%20Friday%20said%20they%20%E2%80%9Caccidentally%20killed%20three%20hostages%E2%80%9D%20during%20fighting%20in%20Gaza%2C%20which%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20was%20%E2%80%9Can%20unbearable%20tragedy%E2%80%9D%20that%20all%20of%20Israel%20is%20grieving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20heart%20goes%20out%20to%20the%20bereaved%20families%20at%20this%20difficult%20time.%20I%20strengthen%20our%20courageous%20soldiers%20engaged%20in%20the%20sacred%20mission%20of%20bringing%20home%20our%20hostages%2C%20while%20risking%20their%20lives%20in%20doing%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20Netanyahu%20added.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20on%20this%20painful%20evening%2C%20we%20will%20dress%20our%20wounds%2C%20learn%20the%20lessons%20and%20continue%20the%20most%20important%20effort%20of%20bringing%20all%20the%20hostages%20home.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20130%20hostages%20remain%20in%20Gaza%20amid%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20operation%20against%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20hostages%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20Gaza%20City%20district%20of%20Shijaiyah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20the%20IDF%20said%20its%20soldiers%20mistakenly%20identified%20three%20Israeli%20hostages%20as%20a%20threat.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20result%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20post%20added%2C%20the%20soldiers%20%E2%80%9Cfired%20toward%20them%20and%20the%20hostages%20were%20killed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20victims%20were%20identified%20as%20Yotam%20Haim%2C%20who%20was%20taken%20from%20Kibbutz%20Kfar%20Aza%2C%20and%20Samer%20Talalka%2C%20who%20was%20taken%20from%20Kibbutz%20Nir%20Am.%20The%20IDF%20said%20it%20was%20withholding%20the%20third%20hostage%E2%80%99s%20name%20at%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bodies%20have%20been%20returned%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20tragic%20incident%2C%20the%20army%20bears%20full%20responsibility%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0Israeli%20military%20spokesman%20Daniel%20Hagari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IDF%20said%20it%20was%C2%A0investigating%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtests%20in%20Israel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScores%20of%20people%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20to%20protest%20the%20death%20of%20the%20three%20hostages%20mistakenly%20killed%20by%20Israeli%20soldiers%20in%20Gaza%2C%20according%20to%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20media%20reports%20and%20images%20on%20television%20showed%20protesters%20blocking%20a%20main%20street%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20city%2C%20demanding%20the%20government%20take%20immediate%20action%20to%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20the%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTheir%20time%20is%20running%20out!%20Bring%20them%20home%20now!%E2%80%9D%20the%20crowd%20was%20heard%20chanting%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%3Cem%3E%C2%A0Times%20of%20Israel%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20victory%20until%20every%20last%20hostage%20is%20released!%E2%80%9D%20was%20also%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20demonstrators%20carried%20placards%20with%20pictures%20of%20the%20hostages%20as%20they%20marched%20toward%C2%A0the%20Israeli%20military%20headquarters%2C%20DPA%20news%20agency%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20protesters%20criticised%20Prime%20Minister%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20government%20for%20not%20doing%20enough%20to%20secure%20their%20release.%20Several%20pressed%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fisrael-and-hamas-hostage-deal-what-do-we-know%2Fa-67518562%5C%22%3Eanother%20hostage%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20was%20implemented%20at%20the%20end%20of%20November%20as%20part%20of%20a%20brief%20cease-fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20240%20hostages%20taken%20by%20Hamas%20during%20its%20October%207%20terror%20attacks%20in%20southern%20Israel%2C%20110%20were%20returned%20as%20part%20of%20the%20cease-fire%20arrangement%2C%20along%20with%20several%20Russian-Israelis%20and%20Thai%20nationals%20and%20a%20Filipino%20freed%20in%20separate%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAl%20Jazeera%20cameraman%20killed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAl%20Jazeera%20said%20Friday%20that%20its%20cameraman%20Samer%20Abu%20Daqqa%20had%20been%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20in%20an%20Israeli%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Qatari%20network%2C%20Abu%20Daqqa%2C%20along%20with%20correspondent%20Wael%20Dahdouh%2C%20were%20reporting%20for%20Al%20Jazeera%20Arabic%20from%C2%A0school%20grounds%20in%20Khan%20Younis%20when%20the%20Israel%20strike%20occurred.%20Khan%20Younis%20is%20a%20major%20city%20in%20southern%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAl%20Jazeera%20reported%20that%20Abu%20Daqa%20was%20a%20resident%20of%20Abasan%20al-Kabira%20near%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20and%20that%20he%20has%20four%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20not%20commented%20on%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Abu%20Daqqa%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20at%20least%2063%20journalists%20had%20been%20killed%20since%20the%20conflict%20erupted%20between%20Hamas%20and%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20according%20to%20the%20media%20freedom%20organisation%2C%20The%20Committee%20to%20Protect%20Journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fisrael-hamas-war-idf-says-it-has-killed-3-hostages%2Flive-67727455%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20clas