%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fstory%2Fthe-reddy-brothers-of-bellary%2F262757%5C%22%3EReddy%20brothers%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20were%20then%20in%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAhead%20of%20the%202014%20elections%2C%20however%2C%20he%20authored%20another%20book%20that%20brought%20him%20into%20the%20good%20books%20of%20the%20BJP.%20The%20book%20was%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENarendra%20Modi%3A%20Yaaru%20Tuliyada%20Haadi%20(Narendra%20Modi%3A%20The%20Man%20Who%20Treads%20a%20Unique%20Path%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%20earned%20him%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20ticket%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20he%20has%20since%20hardened%20his%20political%20posturing%20against%20minorities.%20He%20won%20from%20his%20seat%20again%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202015%2C%20Simha%20wrote%20another%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETipu%20Sultan%3A%20Swatantrya%20Veerana%3F%20(Tipu%20Sultan%3A%20Was%20He%20a%20Freedom%20Fighter%3F)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20fuelling%20Hindutva%20passions%20in%20the%20political%20campaign%20against%20the%2018th-century%20ruler%20of%20Mysore.%20Each%20of%20his%20political%20interventions%20provided%20ammunition%20to%20the%20Hindutva%20workers%20who%20would%20mouth%20contested%20facts%20from%20his%20books.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F16105013%2Fbooks.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F16105013%2Fbooks.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F16105013%2Fbooks-300x150.jpg