e%20Ennore%20estuary%2C%20a%20crucial%20nursery%20for%20fish%20that%20local%20communities%20depend%20on%20for%20their%20livelihoods%2C%20before%20flowing%20out%20into%20the%20sea%2C%20environmentalists%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20state%20government%20departments%20have%20now%20sprung%20into%20action%20to%20stem%20the%20damages%2C%20local%20communities%20are%20bearing%20the%20brunt%2C%20as%20is%20the%20environment.%20The%20CPCL%20has%20employed%20local%20fishermen%20to%20conduct%20the%20clean%20up%20%E2%80%93%20but%20they%20are%20using%20their%20bare%20hands%20to%20scoop%20out%20the%20floating%20toxic%20oil%20in%20plastic%20mugs%2C%20and%20with%20no%20access%20to%20any%20protective%20gear.%20People%20in%20villages%20near%20the%20oil%20spill%20are%20experiencing%20numerous%20physical%20symptoms%20due%20to%20exposure%20to%20the%20toxic%20oil%20and%20air%2C%20such%20as%20skin%20and%20eye%20irritation%20and%20giddiness.%20Fisherfolk%20also%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20fish%20kills%20have%20occurred%20and%20birds%20too%20have%20been%20affected%20in%20both%20the%20river%20and%20estuary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20latest%20reports%20submitted%20to%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20(NGT)%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(TNPCB)%20is%20investigating%20both%20the%20CPCL%20as%20well%20as%20another%20industry%20in%20the%20area%20%E2%80%93%20Toshiba-JSW%20%E2%80%93%20since%20the%20latter%20had%20also%20not%20%E2%80%9Chandled%E2%80%9D%20its%20used%20oil%20appropriately%20and%20could%20have%20also%20contributed%20to%20the%20oil%20spill%20into%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal.%20The%20TNPCB%20told%20the%20NGT%20on%20December%2014%20that%2020%20tonnes%20of%20oil-soaked%20soil%20has%20been%20removed%20from%20the%20area%20so%20far%2C%20as%20have%207%2C000%20liters%20of%20oil%20mixed%20with%20water.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFirst%2C%20denial%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20first%2C%20there%20was%20denial.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Cyclone%20Michaung%20struck%20Chennai%20in%20early%20December%2C%20the%20people%20of%20north%20Chennai%20near%20Ennore%20were%20also%20affected%3A%20water%20swirled%20into%20homes%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20electricity.%20The%20floods%2C%20however%2C%20also%20caused%20an%20oil%20leakage%20into%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal.%20The%20oil%20moved%20downstream%20from%20there%2C%20and%20into%20the%20Kosasthalaiyar%20river.%20From%20here%2C%20the%20oil%20slick%20traveled%20further%20downstream%20with%20the%20current%20and%20into%20the%20Ennore%20estuary%2C%20before%20trailing%20away%20into%20the%20sea.%20Media%20reported%20that%20the%20oil%20spill%20had%20reached%20residential%20areas%20including%20Thiruvotriyur%2C%20Nettukuppam%2C%20and%20Ennorekuppam.%20Though%20residents%20pointed%20fingers%20at%20the%20CPCL%20specifically%2C%20it%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsouth%2Fchennai-oil-spill-cyclone-michaung-after-cyclone-michaung-disaster-blame-game-erupts-over-chennai-oil-spill-4661962%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edenied%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20allegations.%20Precious%20time%20%E2%80%93%20that%20could%20have%20been%20used%20to%20immediately%20stem%20the%20oil%20spread%20%E2%80%93%20was%20thus%20lost.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15223658%2F2023_12_09_13_25_47_314-1-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15223658%2F2023_12_09_13_25_47_314-1-1.jpg%201200w%