nd%20also%20spread%20to%20Ennore%20Creek%20and%20Kosasthalaiyar%20River%20Mouth%20and%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CConsidering%20the%20health%20of%20the%20residents%2C%20and%20also%20the%20flora%20and%20fauna%20and%20aquatic%20life%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20NGT%20also%20constituted%20a%20High-Level%20Committee%20comprising%20nine%20members%20including%20the%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary%20to%20the%20government%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20TNPCB%2C%20district%20collectors%20of%20Chennai%20and%20Thiruvallur%20districts%20and%20the%20Director%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Fisheries%2C%20on%20the%20same%20day.%20It%20ordered%20that%20the%20Committee%20take%20immediate%20action%20to%20arrest%20the%20oil%20spread%2C%20and%20remove%20the%20oil%20from%20the%20affected%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOil%20spill%20spans%20across%2020%20sq%20km%20of%20sea%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20committee%20shall%20also%20get%20the%20damage%20assessment%20undertaken%20and%20arrive%20at%20the%20funds%20required%20for%20remediation%20as%20well%20as%20compensation%2C%20if%20any%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20green%20court%20noted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20team%20of%20the%20state%20environment%20department%20led%20by%20the%20member-secretary%20of%20the%20TNPCB%20finally%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Ftamil-nadu%2F2023%2Fdec%2F12%2Fcpcl-faulted-for-oil-spill-in-ennore-2640789.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eidentified%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20CPCL%20as%20the%20source%20of%20the%20oil%20leakage%2C%20due%20to%20its%20poor%20management%20of%20storm%20water%20drains%20that%20are%20connected%20to%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal.%20Per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20TNPCB%20has%20also%20asked%20the%20CPCL%20to%20implement%20urgent%20mitigation%20measures%20on%20priority%3B%20an%20impact%20study%20of%20affected%20fisherfolk%20families%20is%20underway%20and%20the%20state%20environment%20department%20is%20also%20assessing%20biodiversity%20loss%20in%20the%20area.%20On%20the%20same%20day%2C%20December%2011%2C%20the%20TNPCB%20also%20ordered%20the%20CPCL%20to%20identify%20%E2%80%9Chotspots%E2%80%9D%20of%20oil%20spillage%20in%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal%2C%20Ennore%20estuary%20and%20the%20adjoining%20areas%20and%20take%20remedial%20measures%20immediately%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fchennai%2Ftn-pollution-cpcl-urgent-remedial-ennore-creek-oil-spillage-9064998%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Coast%20Guard%20has%20estimated%20that%20the%20oil%20spill%20has%20trailed%20into%20the%20sea%2C%20covering%20around%2020%20square%20kilometers%20of%20open%20water%2C%20activist%20and%20environmentalist%20Nityanand%20Jayaraman%2C%20of%20the%20Vettiver%20Collective%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20over%20phone.%20However%2C%20the%20extent%20%E2%80%93%20and%20impact%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20oil%20spill%20on%20the%20Kosasthalaiyar%20river%20into%20which%20it%20leaked%20from%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal%2C%20and%20the%20Ennore%20estuary%2C%20are%20still%20unassessed%2C%20Jayaraman%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20estuary%2C%20which%20also%20has%20patches%20of%20mangrove%20cover%2C%20is%20crucial%20for%20fishermen%20because%20it%20serves%20as%20a%20nursery%20for%20fish%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Moreover%2C%20sediments%20along%20the%20estuary%20have%20been%20coated%20with%20oil%2C%20he%20added.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20as%20good%20as%20running%20a%20bulldozer%20through%20the%20%5Bfish%5D%20nursery.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20last%20oil%20spill%20that%20occurred%20off%20the%20Chennai%20coast%20%E2%80%93%20also%20off%20Ennore%2C%20but%20in%20the%20open%20sea%20%E2%80%93%20was%20in%20early%202017%2C%20when%20two%20oil%20tankers%20%E2%80%93%20the%20empty%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBW%20Maple%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20the%20oil-loaded%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDawn%20Kancheepuram%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20collided.%20However%2C%20the%202017%20spill%20is%20not%20comparable%20to%20the%20ongoing%20oil%20spill%20because%20the%20impacts%20caused%20in%20the%20river%20and%20the%20estuary%20are%20very%20different%20when%20compared%20to%20that%20seen%20in%20the%20open%20sea%2C%20said%20Jayaraman.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPeople%20and%20the%20environment%20at%20risk%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFish%20kills%20have%20occurred%20in%20both%20the%20river%20and%20the%20estuary%2C%20said%20R.L.%20Srinivasan%2C%20a%20fisherman%20who%20hails%20from%20the%20nearby%20Kaatukuppam%20fishing%20village%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20eight%20villages%20that%20have%20been%20affected%20by%20the%20oil%20spill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20oil%20spill%20lies%20thick%2C%20like%20a%20wad%20of%20four%20tissue%20papers%2C%20on%20the%20river%20and%20the%20estuary%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CBirds%20in%20the%20area%20too%20have%20been%20coated%20with%20the%20oil%20and%20seem%20to%20be%20affected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Febird.org%2Fhotspot%2FL22559793%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ee-Bird%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20global%20citizen%20science%20platform%20of%20bird%20listings%2C%20Ennore%20creek%20is%20home%20to%20many%20birds%20as%20well%20including%20the%20spot-billed%20pelican%20(a%20species%20that%20is%20listed%20as%20Near%20Threatened%20by%20the%20IUCN%20Red%20List%20of%20Threatened%20Species)%2C%20and%20migratory%20species%20such%20as%20the%20whimbrel%20and%20the%20wood%20sandpiper%2C%20which%20visit%20the%20area%20in%20winters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Kosasthalaiyar%20now%20flows%20black%2C%20like%20a%20sewage%20drain%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Srinivasan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOil%2C%20pushed%20by%20water%20currents%2C%20has%20also%20accumulated%20in%20thick%20layers%20along%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20estuary%20where%20the%20currents%20are%20slower%2C%20both%20Srinivasan%20and%20Jayaraman%20noted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20was%20also%20obvious%20right%20away%20was%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20oil%20spill%20on%20the%20local%20communities%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20oil%20spill%20is%20just%20a%20five%20minute-walk%20from%20my%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srinivasan%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20three%20days%20of%20the%20spill%20%E2%80%93%20with%20no%20electricity%20to%20boot%2C%20due%20to%20Cyclone%20Michaung%20%E2%80%93%20were%20a%20nightmare%2C%20he%20said.%20Most%20people%20in%20his%20village%20complained%20of%20eye%20and%20skin%20irritation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20giddiness%3B%20older%20people%20had%20wheezing%20and%20breathing%20issues%2C%20the%2043-year-old%20said.%20As%20the%20wind%20changed%20direction%2C%20there%20was%20some%20relief%2C%20Srinivsan%20said.%20But%20fishermen%20still%20have%20to%20wade%20through%20oil-covered%20waters%20to%20get%20their%20boats%20going.%20A%20thick%20layer%20of%20oil%20has%20also%20coated%20several%20boats%2C%20making%20it%20impossible%20to%20use%20them%20until%20they%20are%20cleaned.%20According%20to%20Jayaraman%2C%20boats%20belonging%20to%20four%20villages%20have%20been%20badly%20damaged%20this%20way.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20anyway%2C%20there%20is%20no%20point%20going%20fishing%3B%20fish%20catch%20here%20reeks%20of%20oil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENo%20protective%20gear%20for%20workers%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20see%20that%20oil%20leaks%20occur%20now%20and%20then%20from%20industries%20upstream%2C%20but%20this%20time%20it%20has%20been%20very%20different%20because%20of%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20flood%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srinivasan%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20the%20CPCL%20was%20issued%20orders%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20oil%2C%20they%20employed%20fishermen%20to%20do%20it%2C%20Srinivasan%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20that%20the%20CPCL%20knows%20the%20impacts%20of%20the%20toxic%20oil%20on%20people%2C%20they%20do%20not%20let%20their%20staff%20handle%20it%20and%20instead%20make%20us%20do%20the%20dirty%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srinivasan%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20they%20did%20not%20give%20the%20fishermen%20any%20protective%20gear%20to%20use%20while%20doing%20this%20either.%20In%20this%20era%20of%20technology%2C%20how%20can%20you%20say%20there%20are%20no%20machines%20to%20do%20this%3F%20This%20is%20pathetic.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E2017%20buckets!%202023%20bathroom%20mugs!%20Its%20not%20ok%20to%20expose%20fishers%20who%20r%20victims%20of%20CPCLs%20oil%20pollution%20to%20more%20toxins%20in%20name%20of%20clean%20up.%20Is%20this%20SOP%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCMOTamilnadu%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40CMOTamilnadu%3C%2Fa%3E%20Pls%20insist%20on%20PPEs%2Ftraining%20for%20those%20engaged%20in%20spill%20response.%20No%20training.%20No%20safety.%20No%20dignity.%201%2Fn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FOphDxBOEl7%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FOphDxBOEl7%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20NityanandJayaraman%20(%40NityJayaraman)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNityJayaraman%2Fstatus%2F1734515529707364717%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProtective%20gear%20is%20extremely%20important%20for%20any%20person%20engaging%20in%20cleaning%20up%20oil%20slicks%2C%20said%20Jayaraman.%20Fishermen%20are%20scooping%20out%20the%20oil%20with%20plastic%20mugs%20using%20their%20bare%20hands.%20This%20is%20extremely%20dangerous%20for%20the%20people%20involved%2C%20Jayaraman%20said.%20Ideally%2C%20people%20engaged%20in%20the%20clean-up%20should%20be%20given%20the%20right%20masks%20and%20gloves%20and%20other%20protective%20gear%20but%20this%20has%20not%20happened%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20work%20also%20has%20to%20be%20taken%20up%20in%20shifts%20to%20decrease%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20that%20each%20worker%20is%20exposed%20to%20the%20toxic%20air%20and%20oil.%20Another%20crucial%20aspect%20is%20that%20the%20work%20should%20be%20done%20only%20after%20giving%20workers%20detailed%20briefings%20on%20how%20to%20go%20about%20it%20and%20what%20risks%20to%20avoid%20while%20conducting%20the%20clean-up%2C%20said%20Jayaraman.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20four%20ports%20in%20Chennai%2C%20no%20other%20city%20in%20India%20has%20so%20many%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jayaraman%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20four%20ports%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20expertise%20to%20deal%20with%20oil%20spills%20and%20have%20to%20have%20manual%20scavengers%20doing%20the%20job%3F%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20we%20have%20mechanical%20devices%20sucking%20it%20out%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FEnnoreOilSpill%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23EnnoreOilSpill%3C%2Fa%3E%20response%20is%20turning%20an%20environmental%20disaster%20into%20an%20Occupational%20Health%20disaster.%20Not%20the%20way%20to%20handle%20hazwaste.%20Lack%20of%20protocol%20%26amp%3B%20preparedness%20exposing%20workers%20to%20toxic%20%26amp%3B%20physical%20hazards.%20Wrong%20masks%2C%20no%20coveralls%2C%20no%20protocol.%20Dangerous%20ad-hocism.%201%2Fn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FzFguwvLChu%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FzFguwvLChu%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20NityanandJayaraman%20(%40NityJayaraman)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNityJayaraman%2Fstatus%2F1735300355804852297%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVisuals%20of%20flood%20rescue%20workers%20wading%20through%20the%20oil-laced%20waters%2C%20and%20videos%20of%20floods%20waters%20containing%20oil%20flowing%20into%20houses%20near%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal%20were%20what%20prompted%20volunteers%20with%20Suzhal%20Arivom%2C%20a%20Chennai-based%20environmental%20group%2C%20to%20visit%20the%20area%20and%20look%20into%20it%2C%20said%20Deepak%20Venkatachalam%2C%20coordinator%20of%20the%20group.%20Their%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facrobat.adobe.com%2Fid%2Furn%3Aaaid%3Asc%3AAP%3A5cedbaa1-ebee-4e96-b2b6-e8bff18d2f69%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erapid%20assessment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20situation%20conducted%20in%20north%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20affected%20areas%20on%20December%209%20found%20that%20trails%20of%20oil%20were%20still%20coming%20from%20CPCL%20and%20that%20no%20action%20had%20been%20taken%20till%20then%20to%20arrest%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20oil%20into%20the%20river%2C%20estuary%20or%20sea%2C%20Venkatachalam%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98We%20need%20proper%20systems%20in%20place%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20problem%20is%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20have%20learnt%20from%20the%20experience%20in%202017%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Venkatachalam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%202017%20oil%20spill%20off%20Ennore%20spread%20to%20the%20coast%20of%20southern%20Chennai%20and%20beyond%20%E2%80%93%20including%20the%20shores%20of%20Mahabalipuram%20and%20Kalpakkam%20%E2%80%93%20in%20less%20than%20a%20week%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20northeast%20monsoon%20is%20in%20play%2C%20and%20water%20currents%20along%20the%20shore%20run%20north%20to%20south%20during%20this%20time%2C%20the%20oil%20spill%20will%20swiftly%20move%20south%20and%20affect%20the%20shores%20in%20areas%20south%20of%20Ennore%20once%20it%20reaches%20the%20sea%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Venkatachalam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20bodes%20bad%20news%20for%20the%20Olive%20Ridley%20turtles%20that%20visit%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20coasts%20%E2%80%93%20including%20the%20Marina%20and%20Elliot%E2%80%99s%20beaches%20in%20Chennai%20%E2%80%93%20to%20lay%20their%20eggs%20there%2C%20according%20to%20Venkatachalam.%20The%20IUCN%20Red%20List%20classifies%20Olive%20Ridleys%20as%20%E2%80%9Cvulnerable%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20a%20decreasing%20trend%20in%20their%20numbers%20worldwide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15224024%2F2023_12_09_15_30_03_654-1-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15224024%2F2023_12_09_15_30_03_654-1-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-conten