ld%20be%20appropriate%20for%20fishermen%20to%20enter%20into%20the%20sea%2Fbackwaters%20as%20this%20oil%20spillage%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20affected%20the%20livelihood%20of%20the%20fishermen%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20NGT%20noted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20asked%20the%20state%20government%20to%20list%20the%20measures%20that%20they%20have%20taken%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20oil%20spill%20interfering%20with%20fisher%E2%80%99%20livelihoods%20when%20the%20oil%20spill%20made%20it%20impossible%20for%20fisherfolk%20to%20head%20to%20the%20sea%20after%20the%20cyclone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20December%2014%2C%20TNPCB%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgreentribunal.gov.in%2Fgen_pdf_test.php%3Ffilepath%3DL25ndF9kb2N1bWVudHMvbmd0L2Nhc2Vkb2Mvb3JkZXJzL0NIRU5OQUkvMjAyMy0xMi0xNC9jb3VydHMvMS9kYWlseS8xNzAyNjMwMTMxNDY1MzIzNzI0NjU3YzEyZjM2OGQ1ZC5wZGY%3D%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%20the%20NGT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20December%2014%20that%20about%2020%20tonnes%20of%20oil-soaked%20soil%20has%20been%20removed%20so%20far.%20It%20also%20submitted%20that%20around%207%2C000%20liters%20of%20oil%20and%20water%20has%20been%20recovered%20from%20the%20waters%20in%20Ennore%20creek.%20So%20far%2C%2075%20boats%2C%20one%20oil%20skimmer%2C%20and%20four%20JCBs%20are%20currently%20being%20used%20in%20the%20clean%20up%20process%3B%209%2C900%20absorbent%20pads%20have%20also%20been%20used%20to%20absorb%20the%20oil%20from%20the%20water%20surface%2C%20the%20TNPCB%20reported%20to%20the%20NGT.%20Apart%20from%20using%20oil%20skimmers%2C%20ejectors%2C%20gully%20suckers%20as%20well%20as%20bio-dispersal%20sprays%2C%20the%20CPCL%20has%20pressed%20into%20service%20a%20Chennai-based%20agency%20that%20has%20expertise%20in%20oil%20spill%20management%20to%20clear%20the%20oil%20from%20the%20water%20surface%3B%20the%20company%20is%20also%20supposedly%20cleaning%20up%20homes%20and%20schools.%20The%20NGT%20has%20ordered%