e%20authorities%20for%20these%20restrictions%20and%20curbs%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20managing%20body%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20claims%20of%20so-called%20normalcy%20by%20rulers%20fall%20flat%20by%20such%20anti-people%20measures%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mirwaiz%20said%20in%20the%20statement%2C%20denouncing%20the%20curbs%20while%20accusing%20the%20authorities%20of%20allegedly%20targeting%20Jamia%20Masjid%20%E2%80%9Cagain%20and%20again%20%E2%80%A6.%20to%20cause%20grief%20to%20Muslims%20of%20the%20valley%20and%20show%20them%20their%20place%20in%20%E2%80%98naya%20Kashmir%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlluding%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20Centre%2C%20Mirwaiz%20said%20that%20the%20authorities%20should%20%E2%80%9Cstop%20playing%20with%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20the%20Muslims%C2%A0%C2%A0and%20let%20them%20offer%20prayers%20in%20their%20mosques%20without%20hindrance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%E2%80%99s%20silence%20and%20endurance%20of%20brazen%20attacks%20on%20their%20religious%20rights%20should%20not%20be%20mistaken%20as%20their%20weakness%20to%20respond%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mirwaiz%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%202002%20dialogue%20on%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%20with%20Pakistan%20initiated%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20Centre%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%20this%20year%2C%20after%20more%20than%20four%20years%2C%20the%20moderate%20Hurriyat%20chief%20was%20released%20from%20%E2%80%98house%20arrest%E2%80%99%20and%20allowed%20to%20deliver%20the%20Friday%20sermon%20at%20the%20mosque%20in%20Nowhatta%20locality%20of%20downtown%20Srinagar%20which%20used%20to%20be%20a%20separatist%20hotbed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMirwaiz%E2%80%99s%20appearance%20at%20the%20mosque%20had%20triggered%20emotional%20scenes%20as%20he%20stood%20to%20address%20the%20worshippers%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20stripped%20of%20its%20special%20status.%20On%20the%20pulpit%2C%20the%20Hurriyat%2