ment%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334763%2Fchristmas-delicacies-indian-dishes-desserts-cookies-bebinca-neyyappam%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IAS%20Officer%20Saloni%20Sidana%20Shares%20Strategy%20For%20Cracking%20UPSC%20CSE%20in%20First%20Attempt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPresently%20posted%20as%20the%20district%20collector%20of%20Mandla%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20becoming%20an%20IAS%20officer%20was%20never%20a%20life-long%20dream%20for%20Saloni%20Sidana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20doctor%20by%20education%2C%20she%20completed%20her%20MBBS%20from%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Lady%20Hardinge%20Medical%20College%20in%202012.%20Before%20preparing%20for%20the%20UPSC%20CSE%20(Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20Civil%20Services%20Exam)%2C%20Saloni%20received%20an%20opportunity%20to%20move%20abroad%20for%20higher%20studies.%20However%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20stay%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20when%20my%20father%20suggested%20that%20I%20appear%20for%20the%20UPSC%20examination%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saloni%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Jalalabad%20town%20in%20Punjab%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20her%20motivation%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20being%20a%20civil%20servant%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20still%20value%20the%20profession%20of%20a%20doctor.%20The%20commonality%20between%20the%20two%20jobs%20%5Bdoctors%20and%20civil%20servants%5D%20is%20that%20you%20deal%20with%20people.%20Unlike%20many%20other%20professions%20where%20you%20have%20a%20desk%20job%2C%20being%20a%20doctor%20allowed%20me%20to%20deal%20directly%20with%20people%2C%20which%20is%20the%20same%20after%20you%20become%20a%20public%20servant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20UPSC%20allows%20you%20to%20broaden%20your%20knowledge%20horizon.%20If%20I%20had%20been%20just%20a%20doctor%2C%20I%20would%20have%20not%20read%20geogra